hosting-reviews/ipage-review/\">Read our iPage review >></a></p>\n<h2>7. tsoHost</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tso-host.jpg\" alt=\"tsohost-best-uk-web-hosting\" width=\"740\" height=\"364\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234991\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tso-host.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tso-host-300x148.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>tsoHost is a UK based hosting company that are trusted by over 250,000 customers and have been in business for 14 years. </p>\n<p>tsoHost offers fully managed WordPress hosting, 1-click installation, a free domain name, and superior speed. Aside from WordPress hosting, they also offer cloud web hosting, cPanel hosting, VPS hosting, and dedicated server. With VPS and dedicated server web hosting solutions you get a 99.9% uptime guarantee. </p>\n<p>Their shared hosting plans come with a 30-day money back guarantee and theyre also backed by 24/7 expert support through telephone, support tickets, and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-live-chat-software-compared/\">live chat</a>. </p>\n<p><strong>UK Servers</strong>: Yes, London, UK. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Regular pricing starts at 2.92/month. </p>\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hostinger-uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >8. Hostinger</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hostinger-uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/hostinger.jpg\" alt=\"hostinger-uk-web-hosts\" width=\"740\" height=\"411\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234992\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/hostinger.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/hostinger-300x167.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hostinger-uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Hostinger</a> is a European web host, established in 2004, with over 29 million users. They offer shared web hosting which is perfect for small and medium websites, as well as cloud and VPS hosting. </p>\n<p>This web hosting service offers a unique hPanel thats powerful and easy to use, exceptional speed, WordPress optimization, and more. </p>\n<p>Beginners can be at ease with their 24/7/365 live customer support and you can try them out risk-free with their 30-day money back guarantee. </p>\n<p><strong>UK Servers</strong>: Yes, UK. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Regular prices start at 7.99/month. </p>\n<p><strong>Special Offer</strong>: At the time of writing this article, you can get started for as little as 0.80/month. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hostinger-uk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with Hostinger &raquo;</a></p>\n<h2>9. Heart Internet</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/heart-internet.jpg\" alt=\"heart-internet-web-hosting\" width=\"740\" height=\"363\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234993\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/heart-internet.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/heart-internet-300x147.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Heart Internet is the 2nd largest web host in the UK for websites hosted. Heart Internet provides security, reliability, and speed with their UK based network. </p>\n<p>They also offer 1-click WordPress installation and with their starter web hosting plan you get 10GB of web space and 50GB of monthly bandwidth which is fine for beginners. Plus, they offer easy upgrade options as your site grows. </p>\n<p>You can get your issues resolved and questions answered by their friendly support team, 24/7. </p>\n<p><strong>UK Servers</strong>: Yes, UK. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Regular pricing starts at 3.99/month. </p>\n<h2>10. eUKhost</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/eukhost-website.jpg\" alt=\"eUKhost-UK-web-host\" width=\"740\" height=\"363\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234994\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/eukhost-website.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/eukhost-website-300x147.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>eUKhost is based primarily in the UK and theyre trusted by over 35,000 customers around the world. </p>\n<p>Their basic shared web hosting shared plan comes with 2GB of UK disk space, unmetered bandwidth, a free domain name, and more. </p>\n<p>eUKhost also offers highly-rated technical support, 24/7, which is a big part of the reason that theyre rated 9.4 out of 10 on TrustPilot. </p>\n<p><strong>UK Servers</strong>: Yes, Maidenhead, Reading, Nottingham, and Manchester, UK. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Regular pricing starts at 2.78/month. </p>\n<h2>Choosing the Best UK Web Hosting</h2>\n<p>Whether your site is based in the UK or youre making a website meant for mainly UK users, there are a number of factors you need to consider when choosing the best UK web hosting, including:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Latency</li>\n<li>Uptime Guarantee</li>\n<li>Features</li>\n<li>Technical Support</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Lets quickly go over each of them. </p>\n<p><strong>1. Latency</strong><br />\nOne of the most important factors is latency. </p>\n<p>What is latency? Latency is the time span of a server receiving and processing a user-made request. Latency is affected by the location of the web host as well as the location of the website audience. The closer a website or a user is to a data center, the better their page loading time will be. </p>\n<p>So, you can see why looking at the location of the web hosting servers is important. Your website needs to load quickly if you dont want to risk losing out on website visitors. If youre making a UK website, youll want to look for web hosts with servers in the UK or close by. Although, some US-based web hosts are powerful enough to still deliver a speedy loading time. </p>\n<p><strong>2. Uptime Guarantee</strong><br />\nUptime is the measure of time that a server is working and available. If your website experiences a lot of downtime, users wont be able to visit it. This can cause your website visitors to be annoyed and they may even think that your site no longer exists which is why its important to choose a web host that offers a good uptime guarantee. </p>\n<p>Its nearly impossible to guarantee a 100% uptime, but anything below 99.9% is fairly unreliable. </p>\n<p><strong>3. Features</strong><br />\nA good web host should provide you with all the features you need to build a website easily. For instance, some important features include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1-Click Installation &#8211; You should be able to install software such as WordPress in 1-click. </li>\n<li>Website Builder &#8211; Creating a website is much easier with a drag and drop website builder. </li>\n<li>Email Hosting &#8211; As a business, its important to have a business email that matches your domain name. </li>\n<li>Free Domain &#8211; Many web hosts provide a free domain which saves you money when starting out.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Other valuable features include marketing tools, unlimited disk space and bandwidth, control panel, and more. Look closely at the features of the web host to make sure it offers everything you need. </p>\n<p><strong>4. Technical Support</strong><br />\nFor beginners and experts alike, its important to choose a web hosting service that provides solid technical support. Its best to choose a web host that can offer 24/7 support with great response time, that way you dont have to wait around for a callback or a reply. Instead, you can get your issues fixed right away and make sure your website is available to your visitors at all times. </p>\n<p>You should also look at the documentation. A web host that provides a wide range of documentation to help you solve your issues will be helpful to boost your knowledge base and solve your own problems. </p>\n<h2>Recap: Best UK Web Hosting</h2>\n<p>After reviewing all of the best UK web hosting providers, we recommend <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Bluehost</a> as our #1 pick. With Bluehost being one of the most popular web hosting companies in the world, you know your website is in safe hands. </p>\n<p>Bluehost offers numerous pricing plans to fit your needs, a wide range of features, awesome customer support, great performance and uptime, and theyre also affordable.</p>\n\n<table id=\"tablepress-49\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-49\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1 odd\">\n	<th class=\"column-1\">UK Web Hosting</th><th class=\"column-2\">Cost</th><th class=\"column-3\">Money Back</th><th class=\"column-4\">Load Time</th><th class=\"column-5\">Uptime</th><th class=\"column-6\">Support</th><th class=\"column-7\">UK Server</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-2 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Bluehost</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">2.17/month</td><td class=\"column-3\">30 days</td><td class=\"column-4\">689 ms</td><td class=\"column-5\">99.99%</td><td class=\"column-6\">10/10</td><td class=\"column-7\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">SiteGround</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">3.95/month</td><td class=\"column-3\">30 days</td><td class=\"column-4\">649 ms</td><td class=\"column-5\">99.98%</td><td class=\"column-6\">10/10</td><td class=\"column-7\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitw