0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Tools\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"list building\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"lead generation\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"wordpress plugins for lead generation\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/?p=215044\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:628:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress lead generation plugins to grow your sales and revenue? A perfect lead generation plugin helps to collect emails or other contact details of your potential customers, establish a healthy relationship with them, and convert those users into customers. In this article, well share with you 7 best lead [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-lead-generation-plugins-for-wordpress/\">7 Best Lead Generation Plugins for WordPress (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17114:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress lead generation plugins to grow your sales and revenue? </p>\n<p>A perfect lead generation plugin helps to collect emails or other contact details of your potential customers, establish a healthy relationship with them, and convert those users into customers. </p>\n<p>In this article, well share with you 7 best lead generation plugins for your WordPress site. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">1. OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software.jpg\" alt=\"OptinMonster Best Conversion Optimization Software\" width=\"560\" height=\"260\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155241\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software-300x139.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">OptinMonster</a> is the #1 best lead generation software available on the market. It is the most powerful conversion optimization tool you can use on your website to grow your <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/why-collect-emails-benefits-of-building-an-email-list/\">email list</a>, reduce cart abandonment, and optimize conversion rate.  </p>\n<p>OptinMonster allows you to create beautiful lead capture forms easily and display them strategically on your website. It comes with a simple drag and drop popup form builder and 75+ stunning templates to help you make lead generation forms quickly. </p>\n<p>Herere some top features of OptinMonster plugin:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Multiple form types: You can create popups, floating bars, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-add-a-countdown-timer-in-wordpress/\">countdown timers</a>, fullscreen overlays, slide-ins, and more.</li>\n<li>Exit-Intent Technology: Its OptinMonsters signature technology which lets you recover the abandoning visitors into subscribers and customers.</li>\n<li>OnSite Retargeting and Personalization: The OnSite Retargeting feature lets you target repeat visitors with special offers and promotions. Similarly, you can create perfect campaigns for new users, and already purchased customers.</li>\n<li>Page-Level Targeting: This feature lets you segment your email list based on user behavior on your site and create page-specific campaigns.</li>\n<li>Analytics and insights: Allows you to run A/B testing and provides you with actionable insights to create more targeted campaigns\n</ul>\n<p>OptinMonster is a SaaS (Software as a Service) platform which you can connect with your WordPress site with a free plugin. It also integrates well with other website and eCommerce platforms, and <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-email-newsletter-tools-compared-pros-and-cons/\">email marketing services</a>. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starting from $9 / month for Basic plan. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get started with OptinMonster today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">2. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"WPForms Best WordPress Form Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-158461\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin-300x121.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> is the best drag and drop <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\">WordPress form plugin</a>. It allows you to easily create simple <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-contact-form-in-wordpress-the-simple-way/\">contact forms</a> as well as more powerful forms like eCommerce <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-an-order-form-in-wordpress-the-easy-way/\">order forms</a>, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-survey-in-wordpress/\">survey forms</a>, and more for your needs.</p>\n<p>Contact forms are a great way to capture leads. Theyre one of the most used as well as the oldest ways to collect emails and stay in touch with users. Aside from the contact forms, interactive forms like surveys, polls, quizzes, etc. help to collect emails and improve sales. </p>\n<p>Herere top features of WPForms plugin:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Easy to Use: Its the most beginner-friendly WordPress form plugin. You can easily create forms using its drag and drop builder.</li>\n<li>Instant Notifications: You can respond to leads instantly with the Instant Notifications feature and boost user engagement.</li>\n<li>Email Marketing Integration: Integrates well with most of the email marketing providers like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Constant Contact</a> and <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/aweber/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AWeber</a>.</li>\n<li>Easy Payment Options: You can easily collect payments, donations, and online orders with PayPal or Stripe.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starting from $39 / year for Basic plan. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get started with WPForms today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\">3. SeedProd</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/seedprod-coming-soon-page-wordpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"SeedProd Best Coming Soon and Maintenance Mode WordPress Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"280\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-157623\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/seedprod-coming-soon-page-wordpress-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/seedprod-coming-soon-page-wordpress-plugin-300x135.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\">SeedProd</a> is the best coming soon page and maintenance mode plugin for WordPress. It allows you to create stunning coming soon pages in minutes, drive traffic, and grow your email list. </p>\n<p>If youre planning to launch a new business website, then creating a coming soon page helps to make it a big launch with visitors on day 1. The plugin lets you create professional coming soon pages with an email signup form and social media icons to generate leads. </p>\n<p>Herere top SeedProd plugin features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pre-made Coming Soon Themes: It offers 50+ pre-made themes to let you create coming soon pages quickly. Youll also get access to 500,000+ background images and 750+ Google fonts.</li>\n<li>Email Marketing Integration: Smooth integration email service providers like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/mailchimp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">MailChimp</a>, ActiveCampaign, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/convertkit/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">CovertKit</a> and more to let you collect emails.</li>\n<li>Social Sharing: You can add social share buttons on your landing page and also grow social media fans. It also lets you provide an incentive to people who share your site and promote sharing. </li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>:  Starting from $29.60 / year for Basic plan. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get started with SeedProd today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. LiveChat</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/live-chat-software.jpg\" alt=\"LiveChat Best Live Chat Software for WordPress\" width=\"560\" height=\"260\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155284\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/live-chat-software.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/live-chat-software-300x139.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> is the best live chat software in the world. It allows you to easily add live chat on your website and offer your visitors the fastest way to connect with your team. </p>\n<p>By adding live chat on your website, you can offer support, solve users queries, build trust, and generate more eCommerce leads for your business. As youre offering instant help, its easy to collect emails, phone numbers, or other user information with a live chat. </p>\n<p>Herere the top features of LiveChat:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Powerful Chat Tools: Offers the most powerful chat features and tools. It includes message sneak-peek, visitor information, timeline, file sharing, delivery status, and more. </li>\n<li>Customization Options: You can customize your chat application with your company logo, social media buttons, agent profiles, and more.</li>\n<li>Engage Customers: Lets you send automatic greetings, ticket form, chat on Facebook, etc.</li>\n<li>Chat reports: Provides you with your chat reports and daily summary to analyze if your chats are working well or not. </li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starting from $16 / year for Starter plan. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with LiveChat today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Beaver Builder</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/beaver-builder-wordpress-landing-page-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"Beaver Builder Best WordPress Page Builder Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"305\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-157618\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/beaver-builder-wordpress-landing-page-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/beaver-builder-wordpress-landing-page-plugin-300x148.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Beaver Builder</a> is the most popular <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-drag-and-drop-wordpress-page-builders/\">WordPress drag and drop page builder plugin</a>. The plugin lets you create professional-looking WordPress landing pages easily without using any code. </p>\n<p>A good-looking and appealing landing page is the first thing you need to grab user interest. Its more important to have people stay on your website, complete your forms, or buy your products. Beaver Builder is the perfect plugin for that. </p>\n<p>Herere top features of Beaver Builder:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Frontend Drag and Drop Page Builder: Lets you position text, images, and other content easily with frontend drag and drop editor.</li>\n<li>Pre-designed Templates: Beaver Builder comes with dozens of pre-designed page templates ready for use. You can instantly customize these pages and launch your site.</li>\n<li>Call to Action Buttons and Email Subscription Forms: Lets you add an attractive call to action buttons and email subscription forms to generate more leads.</li>\n<li>Works with Any Theme: The plugin is compatible with any WordPress theme youve on your site.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starting from $99 / year for Standard plan.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Beaver Builder today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/formidable-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Formidable Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/formidable-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/formidable-forms.jpg\" alt=\"Formidable Forms Most Advanced WordPress Form Builder Plugin\" width=\"560\" height=\"292\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-149511\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/formidable-forms.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/formidable-forms-300x156.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/formidable-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Formidable Forms</a> is the most advanced WordPress form builder plugin. It allows you to build complex multi-page forms with file uploads, conditional logic and calculations in minutes. </p>\n<p>Its great for creating advanced quizzes, WooCommerce forms, user registration forms, and more.  </p>\n<p>Also, it lets you display the collected data with views and graphs on your WordPress website. </p>\n<p>Herere top features of Formidable Forms:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Drag and Drop Form Builder: Lets you create complex forms in a simple drag and drop interface.</li>\n<li>Multilingual Forms: Seamless integration witn WPML lets you translate your forms into multiple languages and collect both local and international leads.</li>\n<li>Email Marketing: It lets you connect your website with popular email providers like MailChimp, ActiveCampaign etc. and collect more email subscribers.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starting from $99 / year for Creator plan. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/formidable-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Formidable Pro today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/thriveleads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Thrive Leads</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/thriveleads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/thriveleadsplugin.png\" alt=\"Thrive Leads List Building and Popup WordPress Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"322\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-211605\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/thriveleadsplugin.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/thriveleadsplugin-300x156.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/thriveleads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Thrive Leads</a> is one of the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-popup-plugins/\">most popular WordPress popup plugins</a> on the internet. It allows you to create beautiful email optin forms and build your email list faster. </p>\n<p>Similar to OptinMonster, it lets you create different types of optin forms, including lightbox popups, slide-ins, scroll mat, and yes/no multiple choice forms. However, it misses out the powerful targeting features like OnSite retargeting, geo-location targeting, and more. </p>\n<p>Another difference is that its a WordPress-only plugin. So, if you prefer to handle everything from your dashboard, then you can use this plugin as OptinMonster alternative. </p>\n<p>Herere top features of Thrive Leads: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Eye-catching Templates: Quickly build effective lead generation and list building forms with pre-made templates.</li>\n<li>Advanced A/B Testing: Offers an A/B testing engine to help you design the best possible optin form design.</li>\n<li>Personalization and targeting: Lets you show different content for a different visitor and generate more leads.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starting from $67 / year for 1 license. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/thriveleads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Thrive Leads today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to find the best lead generation plugin for your WordPress site. You may also want to see our ultimate list of the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers/\">best WordPress plugins</a> to grow your business faster. </p>\n<p>And dont forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more helpful WordPress articles and Google Analytics tips.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-lead-generation-plugins-for-wordpress/\">7 Best Lead Generation Plugins for WordPress (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-lead-generation-plugins-for-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"24 Best WooCommerce Plugins to Grow Your Traffic and Sales (2019)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:155:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-woocommerce-plugins-and-extensions/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=best-woocommerce-plugins-and-extensions\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-woocommerce-plugins-and-extensions/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 08 Jul 2019 14:09:58 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Tools\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"woocommerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WooCommerce tools\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"WooCommerce Marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/?p=191096\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:656:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WooCommerce plugins and extensions for your online store? WooCommerce is the official plugin for building an eCommerce site in WordPress. However, it doesnt include all the advanced features youll need to run a full-fledged online shop on its own. Thats where WooCommerce plugins and extensions come in handy. Therere [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-woocommerce-plugins-and-extensions/\">24 Best WooCommerce Plugins to Grow Your Traffic and Sales (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34328:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WooCommerce plugins and extensions for your online store? <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WooCommerce</a> is the official plugin for building an eCommerce site in WordPress. However, it doesnt include all the advanced features youll need to run a full-fledged online shop on its own.</p>\n<p>Thats where WooCommerce plugins and extensions come in handy. Therere tons of powerful plugins and tools available to add useful features to your <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-woocommerce-store/\">WooCommerce store</a>, and help boost your sales.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the 24 best WooCommerce plugins and extensions to grow your eCommerce store faster.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">1. MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-186638\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/monsterinsightsbestgapluginforwordpress.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights Best Google Analytics Plugin for WordPress\" width=\"620\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/monsterinsightsbestgapluginforwordpress.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/monsterinsightsbestgapluginforwordpress-300x155.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">MonsterInsights</a> is the most popular Google Analytics plugin for WordPress. It tracks your eCommerce site visitors online behavior and provides you with detailed reports on exactly how theyre interacting with your store.</p>\n<p>The plugin comes with a powerful <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/addon/ecommerce/\">eCommerce addon</a> for tracking the performance of your WordPress stores. It lets you easily <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-track-ecommerce-sales-in-google-analytics/\"> track your eCommerce sales</a>. Some of the key eCommerce reports include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-find-your-most-popular-ecommerce-products-in-google-analytics/\">Most Popular eCommerce Products in your store</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-find-your-average-ecommerce-order-value-in-google-analytics/\">Average eCommerce Order Value</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/which-traffic-source-generates-the-most-revenue/\">Traffic source that generates the most revenue</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/google-analytics-lifetime-value-report-for-woocommerce/\"> Lifetime value of your WooCommerce shop</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/google-analytics-lifetime-value-report-for-woocommerce/\">Individual WooCommerce customer tracking</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once you have all these important reports in hand, you can make data-driven decisions to boost your WooCommerce sales.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">2. OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155241\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software.jpg\" alt=\"optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software\" width=\"560\" height=\"260\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software-300x139.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">OptinMonster</a> is the most powerful, most popular lead generation software available on the market. It helps you convert your website visitors into subscribers to grow your email list faster.</p>\n<p>OptinMonster comes with highly effective features including its signature feature,<a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/exit-intent/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Exit-intent technology</a>. It&#8217;s a smart behavioral technology that monitors the movement of your site visitors and prompts them with a targeted campaign at the exact moment they&#8217;re about to exit your site.</p>\n<p>You can use this feature to reduce cart abandonment and increase sales in your WooCommerce store.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-wishlist/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">3. YITH WooCommerce Wishlist</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-wishlist/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191101\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommercewishlist.png\" alt=\"YITH WooCommerce Wishlist Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommercewishlist.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommercewishlist-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-wishlist/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YITH WooCommerce Wishlist</a> is a cool WooCommerce extension plugin to improve the user experience and indirect sales of your store.</p>\n<p>The plugin allows shoppers to create a wishlist of the products they want to buy. This is useful during the holiday season when people are making shopping lists and buying gifts.</p>\n<p>Also, visitors can share their wishlist via email or social media. This helps to increase your sales indirectly as friends and relatives of your customers use the list to buy .</p>\n<h3><a href=\"ttps://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">4. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"ttps://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-158461\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin-300x121.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"ttps://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WPForms</a> is a simple drag and drop form builder plugin for WordPress. It allows you to create a variety of online forms, including advanced forms like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-survey-in-wordpress/\">surveys</a>and<a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/plugins/how-to-create-conversational-forms-in-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">conversational forms</a>, easily without using any code.</p>\n<p>With WPForms, you can quickly build a beautiful contact form page for your online store. When your users/customers want to ask you anything, they can contact you via your contact page.</p>\n<p>Besides, you can create surveys and quizzes to improve your user engagement. Conversational surveys also offer a fun way to collect user feedback about your products.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://yoast.com/wordpress/plugins/yoast-woocommerce-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">5. Yoast WooCommerce SEO Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://yoast.com/wordpress/plugins/yoast-woocommerce-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-124474\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Yoast-WooCommerce-SEO.2.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Marketing Tools - Yoast WooCommerce SEO\" width=\"560\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Yoast-WooCommerce-SEO.2.png 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Yoast-WooCommerce-SEO.2-300x155.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you want your website to be found in search results, you need to focus on your sites SEO.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re already using the popular <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yoast SEO </a>plugin, you might want to check out the glue that holds WooCommerce and your SEO plugin together, <a href=\"https://yoast.com/wordpress/plugins/yoast-woocommerce-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WooCommerce SEO</a>.</p>\n<p>Not only does this marketing tool optimize your website like the free Yoast SEO plugin, but it also takes things one step further and optimizes it for WooCommerce itself. This gives your marketing efforts the push needed to get ahead of the competition.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Share products on Pinterest as Rich Pins for a better viewing and sharing experience</li>\n<li>Exclude unnecessary information on your shops sitemap that may get in the way of proper indexing and search rankings</li>\n<li>Utilize the breadcrumbs feature, which is better than the default WooCommerce option</li>\n<li>Never forget to optimize for WooCommerce in the edit page because it comes before anything else</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking to maximize your SEO efforts you might want to consider investing in this SEO plugin.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-product-reviews-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">6. WooCommerce Product Reviews Pro</a></h3>\n<p>Claiming that 70% of your customers will view a review before finalizing their purchase, the team at WooCommerce created an extension that allows you to accept product reviews from customers, complete with images and video.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommerceproductreviewsplugin.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Product Reviews Plugin\" width=\"550\" height=\"337\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214304\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommerceproductreviewsplugin.png 550w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommerceproductreviewsplugin-300x184.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-product-reviews-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WooCommerce Product Reviews Pro</a> also lets your customers filter reviews by star ratings, flag reviews that need moderation, upvote or downvote reviews, and boost user interaction. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/affiliate-royale/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Affiliate Royale</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/affiliate-royale/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/affiliateroyale.png\" alt=\"Affiliate Royale Best WordPress Affiliate Program Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-212250\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/affiliateroyale.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/affiliateroyale-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/affiliate-royale/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Affiliate Royale</a> is a powerful affiliate program plugin for WordPress. It comes with seamless integration with WooCommerce that you can create and run a full-fledged affiliate program on your WooCommerce store. </p>\n<p>This WooCommerce affiliate marketing solution helps boost traffic, rank your store higher in search results, and generate more revenue as others promote your online shop for you.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-multilingual/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">8. WooCommerce Multilingual</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-multilingual/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191105\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercemultilingual.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Multilingual plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercemultilingual.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercemultilingual-300x99.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-multilingual/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WooCommerce Multilingual</a> is a translation management plugin for WooCommerce. It comes as an extension of the WPML WordPress Multilingual plugin for WooCommerce-based websites.</p>\n<p>It helps you to translate your WooCommerce products, categories, and everything throughout the checkout process into the language of your choice. You can also send emails to clients and admins in the same language.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-points-and-rewards/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">9. WooCommerce Points and Rewards</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-points-and-rewards/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercepointsrewardsplugin.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Points and Rewards Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214306\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercepointsrewardsplugin.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercepointsrewardsplugin-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Rewarding loyal customers is a great way to encourage them to refer their friends and family, write a positive review, or sign up for your email list. And the great thing is, this helps with WooCommerce automation because your customers do all the work for you.</p>\n<p>WooCommerce Points and Rewards is a WooCommerce extension plugin which lets you provide loyalty points to your customers which they can redeem for discounts. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/recommendation-engine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow rel= noopener\">10. WooCommerce Recommendation Engine</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/recommendation-engine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow rel= noopener\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercereceommendationengineplugin.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Recommendation Engine Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"356\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214307\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercereceommendationengineplugin.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercereceommendationengineplugin-300x172.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you really want to boost the number of sales you generate on your site, use this <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/recommendation-engine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow rel= noopener\">product recommendation extension </a>and start showing customers related products they may be interested in. </p>\n<p>Base the recommendations on purchase history, product views, what others have viewed, and what is often bundled and purchased together.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-ajax-search/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">11. YITH WooCommerce Ajax Search</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-ajax-search/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191106\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommerceajaxsearch.png\" alt=\"YITH WooCommerce Ajax Search\" width=\"620\" height=\"291\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommerceajaxsearch.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommerceajaxsearch-300x141.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-ajax-search/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YITH WooCommerce Ajax Search</a> plugin helps your customers to find what theyre looking for in your store quickly. Instead of browsing across the entire store, they can search for a product they want and buy it instantly.</p>\n<p>The plugin displays search results immediately as users start typing a product name in the search field. It&#8217;s super fast and highly efficient.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-products-slider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">12. PP WooCommerce Products Slider</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-products-slider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191109\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommerceproductslider.png\" alt=\"PP WooCommerce Product Slider\" width=\"620\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommerceproductslider.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommerceproductslider-300x99.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-products-slider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">PP WooCommerce Products Slider</a> lets you create beautiful sliders to display your products in eye-catching new ways. You can add your best products to the product sliders and carousels to instantly visually engage your users.</p>\n<p>Using the plugin, you can create as many sliders as you want and show them anywhere on your website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-compare/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">13. YITH WooCommerce Compare</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-compare/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191110\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yithwoocommercecompare.png\" alt=\"YITH WooCommerce Compare Pllugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yithwoocommercecompare.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yithwoocommercecompare-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-compare/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YITH WooCommerce Compare</a> plugin lets your users compare 2 or more products side-by-side so they can make informed buying decisions.</p>\n<p>Often, shoppers cannot decide which product to buy as they find multiple products of the same nature. At such times of confusion, this simple comparison feature helps them quickly find out which product best suits their needs.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yith-woocommerce-gift-cards/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">14. YITH WooCommerce Gift Cards</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yith-woocommerce-gift-cards/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191112\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yithwoocommercegiftcards.png\" alt=\"YITH WooCommerce Gift Cards Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yithwoocommercegiftcards.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yithwoocommercegiftcards-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yith-woocommerce-gift-cards/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YITH WooCommerce Gift Cards</a> allows your users to purchase gift cards of any amount and send them to their friends and relatives as a gift. The gift cards are prepaid vouchers which will enable their recipients to buy things from your store.</p>\n<p>With gift cards, your customers have a low stress option to show others they care. They won&#8217;t have to deal with the anxiety and confusion of picking out a specific product. On the other hand, the gift card recipients can now buy a product of their choice. Everyone wins!</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woocommerce-discount-rules/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">15. Discount Rules for WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woocommerce-discount-rules/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191113\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/discountrulesforwoocommerce.png\" alt=\"Discount Rules for WooCommerce Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"214\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/discountrulesforwoocommerce.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/discountrulesforwoocommerce-300x104.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Discounts are one of the best ways to boost user interest and increase sales. Because everyone loves getting a deal, you can ultimately sell more by offering discounts.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woocommerce-discount-rules/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Discount Rules for WooCommerce</a> allows you to create dynamic pricing and discounts in your WooCommerce store easily. You can offer a store-wide global discount, cart discounts, special offers, and more with this plugin.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-pdf-invoices-packing-slips/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">16. WooCommerce PDF Invoices &amp; Packing Slips</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-pdf-invoices-packing-slips/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191114\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercepdfinvoices.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce PDF Invoices and Packing Slips\" width=\"620\" height=\"202\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercepdfinvoices.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercepdfinvoices-300x98.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-pdf-invoices-packing-slips/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WooCommerce PDF Invoices &amp; Packing Slips</a> is a free extension for WooCommerce. It automatically adds a PDF invoice to the order confirmation emails sent out to your customers.</p>\n<p>It also makes the PDF invoices and packing slips available in your customers account area. They can easily download or print them from there.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-quick-view/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">17. YITH WooCommerce Quick View</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-quick-view/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191115\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommerce-quick-view.png\" alt=\"YITH WooCommeerce Quick View Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommerce-quick-view.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommerce-quick-view-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-quick-view/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YITH WooCommerce Quick View</a> allows you to add a quick view option for WooCommerce products. A quick view lets your customers see a product&#8217;s details instantly with a click or a mouse hover.</p>\n<p>This feature saves your customers time by not having to open and load a new page for each product that piques their curiosity. It improves user experience and helps to boost your store&#8217;s sales.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">18. YITH WooCommerce Request a Quote</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191117\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommercerequestaquote.png\" alt=\"YITH WooCommerce Request a Quote Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommercerequestaquote.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommercerequestaquote-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>One of the disadvantages of online shopping is the lack of negotiation, but that will no longer be an issue with <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YITH WooCommerce Request a Quote</a> plugin.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a WooCommerce extension plugin by YITH which allows you to add a Quote Request button to your store. Using the button, your customers can send a quote request to you for price negotiation.</p>\n<p>This is useful when your customers want to buy large quantities of the same product, and they want a discount on the price. The plugin enables negotiation option for bulk buyers.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/google-product-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">19. Google Product Feed</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/google-product-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/gproductfeedwoocommerceextension.png\" alt=\"Google Product Feed WooCommerce Extension\" width=\"620\" height=\"356\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214310\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/gproductfeedwoocommerceextension.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/gproductfeedwoocommerceextension-300x172.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Google Product Feed plugin lets you create a real-time feed of your WooCommerce stores products and services to the Google Merchant Center as a unique way of advertising. </p>\n<p>In fact, this extension automates the entire process of feeding product information to Google. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mailchimp-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">20. MailChimp for WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mailchimp-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191104\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/mailchimpforwoocommerce.png\" alt=\"MailChimp for WooCommerce plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"219\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/mailchimpforwoocommerce.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/mailchimpforwoocommerce-300x106.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>MailChimp is one of the most popular email marketing services available on the market. Their official WooCommerce plugin is <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mailchimp-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">MailChimp for WooCommerce</a>.</p>\n<p>When installed on your WooCommerce website, the plugin automatically syncs your customers and their purchase data with your MailChimp account. Then, you can send targeted email campaigns to them and make more sales.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woomarketing-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">21. WooMarketing Bundle</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woomarketing-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191118\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-marketing-bundle.png\" alt=\"WooMarketing Bundle Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"286\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-marketing-bundle.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-marketing-bundle-300x138.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As its name suggests, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woomarketing-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WooMarketing Bundle</a> is a package of WooCommerce marketing extensions. It&#8217;s an official plugin from the WooCommerce team themselves.</p>\n<p>The bundle plugin includes email marketing, Facebook Ads integration, smarter discounts, transactional emails, social logins, etc.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s an excellent offer if you want to implement all the marketing features included in it. Because buying separate plugins for each feature would cost you a lot more than purchasing this single plugin.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woocommerce-pack-and-ship-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">22. WooCommerce Pack &amp; Ship Bundle</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woocommerce-pack-and-ship-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191119\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-pack-and-ship-bundle.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Pack and Ship Bundle\" width=\"620\" height=\"286\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-pack-and-ship-bundle.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-pack-and-ship-bundle-300x138.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WooCommerce Pack &amp; Ship Bundle is a complete package plugin that enables you to sell, pack, and ship products worldwide. It&#8217;s also an official plugin from Team WooCommerce.</p>\n<p>The plugin comes with powerful features including responsive 360-degree image rotation, invoices, packing lists, product kits, multi-address shipping and tracking, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://hootsuite.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">23. Hootsuite</a></h3>\n<p>Utilizing the power of social media can expand your brand to a wider customer base and bring more traffic to your WooCommerce shop.</p>\n<p>However, running an online shop requires a lot of work. From administrative tasks to fulfilling orders, there&#8217;s not a lot of time to promote your company the way you want to.</p>\n<p>Thats where <a href=\"https://hootsuite.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Hootsuite</a> comes in handy.</p>\n<p>In fact, Hootsuite helps with WooCommerce marketing automation by allowing you to schedule your social media posts in advance on up to 30 different social media platforms.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-124458\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Hootsuite.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Marketing Tools - Hootsuite\" width=\"560\" height=\"385\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Hootsuite.png 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Hootsuite-300x206.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>Not only does this save you time, but it also helps you gain more leads that can convert into sales.</p>\n<p>Not to mention you can communicate directly with your team in the Hootsuite dashboard, view detailed analytics reports, and use pre-written responses, automating your marketing process even more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/product-import-export-for-woo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">24. Product Import Export for WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/product-import-export-for-woo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191121\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/productimportexportpluginforwoocommerce.png\" alt=\"Product Import Export for WooCommerce\" width=\"620\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/productimportexportpluginforwoocommerce.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/productimportexportpluginforwoocommerce-300x99.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/product-import-export-for-woo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Product Import Export for WooCommerce</a> allows you to import or export simple products in CSV format. If you need to send your product details to someone, the export feature comes in handy.</p>\n<p>Using this plugin, you can bulk upload and update products in your WooCommerce store. Hence, you dont need to enter data for every single product manually.</p>\n<p>So, thats it! The list of the 24 best WooCommerce plugins and extensions for maximizing your WooCommerce store revenue. We hope this article helped you to choose the plugins most useful for your website.</p>\n<p>You might also want to check out our list of the<a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers/\">best WordPress plugins for every website</a> (free + premium).</p>\n<p>Also, dont forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more WooCommerce guides and Google Analytics tutorials.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-woocommerce-plugins-and-extensions/\">24 Best WooCommerce Plugins to Grow Your Traffic and Sales (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-woocommerce-plugins-and-extensions/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"7 Best WordPress LMS Plugins: Which Is Best for You?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:129:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-lms-plugins/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=best-wordpress-lms-plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-lms-plugins/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 04 Jul 2019 13:44:11 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Tools\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"LMS plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"create WordPress online course\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"free lms plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"wordpress course plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/?p=213686\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:585:\"<p>Are you looking to create an online course in WordPress? Want to know which is the best WordPress LMS plugin? An LMS (Learning Management System) plugin is a piece of WordPress software with an ability to create and run an online course in WordPress. LMS plugins help you to build a website like Udemy, Treehouse, [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-lms-plugins/\">7 Best WordPress LMS Plugins: Which Is Best for You?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17058:\"<p>Are you looking to create an online course in WordPress? Want to know which is the best WordPress LMS plugin? </p>\n<p>An LMS (Learning Management System) plugin is a piece of WordPress software with an ability to create and run an online course in WordPress. LMS plugins help you to build a website like Udemy, Treehouse, DigitalMarketer, etc. and earn money by selling online courses. </p>\n<p>In this article, well compare the 7 best WordPress LMS plugins 2019 to help you choose the best one for your needs. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/learndash/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. LearnDash</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/learndash/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/learndashlmspluginwordpress.png\" alt=\"LearnDash Best WordPress LMS Management Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-194246\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/learndashlmspluginwordpress.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/learndashlmspluginwordpress-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/learndash/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LearnDash</a> is the most popular LMS plugin for WordPress. Trusted by Fortune 500 companies, top universities, and training centers, it offers simply the best way to create and sell online courses with WordPress. </p>\n<p>Herere the top features of LearnDash plugin. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Powerful drag and drop course builder for creating multi-layer courses.</li>\n<li>Drip-feed (schedule) content options  X Days after enrollment or specific date.</li>\n<li>Create advanced quizzes using 8 different question types.</li>\n<li>Award learners with points, certificates, and badges and encourage learning.</li>\n<li>Set one-time price, subscriptions, or membership access to your courses.</li>\n<li>Accept payments with popular payment gateways including PayPal, Stripe, and 2Checkout.</li>\n<li>Front-end user profiles for students to track their course activity.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>LearnDash is a leader in the e-learning industry. Their team offers expert support via support tickets. They also have extensive documentation with easy to use guides and tutorials. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starting from $159 / year for 1 site license. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/learndash/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with LearnDash today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/lifterlms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. LifterLMS</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/lifterlms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/lifterlms.png\" alt=\"LifterLMS Powerful LMS Plugin for WordPress\" width=\"620\" height=\"310\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213732\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/lifterlms.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/lifterlms-300x150.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/lifterlms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LifterLMS</a> is a powerful online course builder software for WordPress sites. It comes with a full set of tools to let you create, sell, and protect engaging online courses in WordPress. </p>\n<p>Herere the top features of LifterLMS plugin. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Supports multimedia including video, audio, text, and images for lessons. </li>\n<li>User-friendly multi-tier drag and drop course builder for creating lessons fast.</li>\n<li>Content dripping and course prerequisites to deliver content over time.</li>\n<li>Create multimedia quizzes, set quiz timer, and engage students.</li>\n<li>Multi instructor support, and discussion areas.</li>\n<li>One-time payment or recurring payments, sell course bundles, coupons, etc.</li>\n<li>Offer achievement badges, certificates, and boost engagement.</li>\n<li>Integrates well with <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\">WordPress form plugins</a>, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-email-newsletter-tools-compared-pros-and-cons/\">email marketing tools</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>LifterLMS offers dedicated customer support via live chat, support tickets, and detailed documentation on their website. </p>\n<p>An advantage of using LifterLMS is that you can easily track your LifterLMS eCommerce data with MonsterInsights Google Analytics plugin. MonsterInsights seamlessly <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/announcing-monsterinsights-7-7-lifterlms-integration/\">integrates with LifterLMS</a> and lets you set up tracking with just one click. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Individual addons for $99 each / year or Universe Bundle for $299 / year (Free version is also available).  </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/lifterlms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with LifterLMS today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/teachable/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Teachable</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/teachable/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/teachable.png\" alt=\"Teachable Powerful Online Course Builder Platform\" width=\"620\" height=\"386\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213733\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/teachable.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/teachable-300x187.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/teachable/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Teachable</a> is yet another powerful online course builder plugin available on the market. Unlike LearnDash and LifterLMS, its a standalone SaaS (Software as a Service) platform for online course creation. </p>\n<p>However, you can easily add your Teachable online courses to your WordPress site by using a subdomain. Or you can simply start with a Teachable subdomain like www.yourschool.teachable.com. </p>\n<p>Herere the top features of Teachable.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Allows you to create engaging multimedia lectures using video, image, audio, and PDF files.</li>\n<li>Powerful course editor for creating beautiful course pages.</li>\n<li>Lets you create quizzes, discussion forums, and issue course completion certificates.</li>\n<li>Use coupons and promotions to boost your sales.</li>\n<li>Create your own affiliate program and reward others for helping you grow your sales.</li>\n<li>Accept payments from 130+ international currencies through PayPal or Stripe.</li>\n<li>Seamless integration with marketing tools like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/mailchimp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">MailChimp</a>, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/aweber/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AWeber</a>, etc.</li>\n<li>Built-in reporting tools to view total sales, revenue, and students progress.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Teachable is a fully hosted platform, so you dont need to worry about backups and updates. The Teachable team offers 24/7 monitoring to keep your online courses up and running. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starting from $29 / month.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/teachable/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Teachable today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://flyplugins.com/wp-courseware/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. WP Courseware</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://flyplugins.com/wp-courseware/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpcourseware.png\" alt=\"WP Courseware Best WordPress Online Course Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"374\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213734\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpcourseware.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpcourseware-300x181.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://flyplugins.com/wp-courseware/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WP Courseware</a> is yet another popular online course creation tool for WordPress. It offers a hassle-free way to create online courses with the drag and drop course builder. </p>\n<p>Herere the top features of WP Courseware. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Drip (schedule) content to be realeased by date or at specific intervals.</li>\n<li>Create powerful quizzes using timers, retake limits, reporting, and surveys.</li>\n<li>Quiz grade books to view quiz results, progress reports of students.</li>\n<li>Provide downloadable and customizable course certificates.</li>\n<li>Easy to integrate with eCommerce and membership plugins.</li>\n<li>Built-in shopping cart with options to connect Stripe or PayPal.</li>\n<li>Works well with most WordPress themes.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>WP Courseware offers support via Member Portal, which is a support hub for their logged in users. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starting from $129 / year for 2-site license.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://flyplugins.com/wp-courseware/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with WP Courseware today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/wordpress-lms-plugin-learnpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. LearnPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/wordpress-lms-plugin-learnpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/learnpress.png\" alt=\"LearnPress Free WordPress LMS Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"230\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213735\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/learnpress.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/learnpress-300x111.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/wordpress-lms-plugin-learnpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LearnPress</a> is a free WordPress LMS plugin available on WordPress.org plugin repository. You can download and use it on as many sites as you like completely for free. However, youll need to buy their premium addons for advanced features. </p>\n<p>Herere the top features of LearnPress plugin.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Create unlimited courses, lessons, quizzes, and questions with ease.</li>\n<li>Add text, images, PowerPoint slideshow, documents, and anything to your lessons.</li>\n<li>Set requirements for students to take a lesson with premium addons like Content Drip and Prerequisite.</li>\n<li>Monitor learners progress, scores, and results with Gradebook addon.</li>\n<li>Use LearnPress WooCommerce for eCommerce features, and payment settings.</li>\n<li>Supports Stripe, 2Checkout, Authorize.Net, and more for accepting payments.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>LearnPress users can get support via forum. Free users can use WordPress.org support forum while paid users have access to a more dedicated support forum on their site. You can also use their documentation page for frequently asked general support queries. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free. (Paid addons available for advanced features)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/wordpress-lms-plugin-learnpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with LearnPress today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/sensei/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. WooCommerce Sensei</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/sensei/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/woocommercesensei.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Sensei WordPress LMS Plugin Free\" width=\"620\" height=\"290\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213736\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/woocommercesensei.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/woocommercesensei-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/sensei/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce Sensei</a> is powerful WordPress LMS plugin built by the team behind WooCommerce. Its a free LMS plugin which enables you to launch your online course without hiring a WordPress developer. </p>\n<p>Herere the top Sensei features.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Beginner-friendly LMS platform for building a WordPress training site.</li>\n<li>Seamless WooCommerce integration and powerful addons to add features.</li>\n<li>Create engaging quizzes that help to strengthen the learners understanding.</li>\n<li>Many free and paid addons available to expand the features of the plugin.</li>\n<li>BuddyPress for Sensei addon helps you turn your course website into social education platform.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>WooCommerce for Sensei users find answers of commonly asked questions in their FAQ page. For technical support, you can log into the plugin forum on WordPress.org or contact WooCommerce team.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free. (Paid addons available for advanced features)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/sensei/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with WooCommerce Sensei today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tutor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Tutor LMS</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tutor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tutorlms.png\" alt=\"Tutor LMS Free WordPress Learning Management System LMS Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"200\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213737\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tutorlms.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/tutorlms-300x97.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tutor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tutor LMS</a> is a free WordPress LMS plugin you can use to create, manage, and sell online courses. Like most LMS plugins, it comes with a user-friendly course builder which lets you create a full-fledged online school and offer education to the students. </p>\n<p>Herere the top Tutor LMS features.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Create unlimited courses and lessons easily.</li>\n<li>Add video lessons self-hosted on your server, or embed from YouTube and Vimeo.</li>\n<li>Frontend student dashboard </li>\n<li>Create advanced quizzes with quiz timer, and quiz attempts.</li>\n<li>Course review and rating system.</li>\n<li>Show course difficulty level, course duration, and also trailer / teaser.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For support, you can post your questions in the support forum on WordPress.org or their website. Also, you can see their simple tutorials on the documentation. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tutor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Tutor LMS plugin today!</a></p>\n<h3>Which is the Best WordPress LMS Plugin</h3>\n<p>After reviewing the most popular LMS plugins available, we conclude that <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/learndash/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LearnDash</a> is the best choice for creating and selling online courses. With its advanced features and powerful integrations, its the WINNER of LMS plugin comparison. </p>\n<p>A close competitor, as well as a perfect LearnDash alternative, is the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/lifterlms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LifterLMS</a> plugin. Similar to LearnDash, it includes advanced features which let you build a great learning center with WordPress. </p>\n<p>An exclusive advantage of using LifterLMS is that you can track your plugin eCommerce data easily using <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/addon/ecommerce/\">MonsterInsights eCommerce addon</a>. </p>\n<p>If you want to use a standalone LMS software, then <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/teachable/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Teachable</a> is the right tool for you. LearnPress, WooCommerce Sensei and Tutor LMS are great plugins for users looking for a free LMS tool. </p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to find the best LMS plugins for WordPress. You may also want to see our handpicked list of <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-popup-plugins/\">best WordPress popup plugins</a>. </p>\n<p>And dont forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more useful WordPress showcases and Google Analytics tips.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-lms-plugins/\">7 Best WordPress LMS Plugins: Which Is Best for You?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-lms-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"How to Track Form Abandonment in WordPress (The Easy Way)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:161:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-track-form-abandonment-in-wordpress/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-to-track-form-abandonment-in-wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-track-form-abandonment-in-wordpress/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 01 Jul 2019 18:34:17 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"forms tracking\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"forms addon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"tracking form abandonment\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"wordpress forms tracking\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/?p=213080\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:608:\"<p>Do you want to track form abandonment on your WordPress site? As forms are major points of interaction on a website, tracking form abandonment on your site lets you know how well users are engaged with your forms and other content. In this article, well show you how to easily track form abandonment in WordPress [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-track-form-abandonment-in-wordpress/\">How to Track Form Abandonment in WordPress (The Easy Way)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12408:\"<p>Do you want to track form abandonment on your WordPress site? </p>\n<p>As forms are major points of interaction on a website, tracking form abandonment on your site lets you know how well users are engaged with your forms and other content. </p>\n<p>In this article, well show you how to easily track form abandonment in WordPress (The Easy Way). </p>\n<h3>Tracking Form Abandonment in WordPress (The Easy Way)</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/the-complete-beginners-guide-to-google-analytics-for-wordpress/\">Google Analytics</a> is the most widely used web analytics tool for tracking website traffic, conversions, and more. </p>\n<p>It lets you track a wide variety of metrics including <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-track-ecommerce-sales-in-google-analytics/\">eCommerce transactions</a>, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-track-your-wordpress-form-conversions-in-google-analytics/\">form conversions</a>, form abandonment, and more, however using it is a bit tricky. </p>\n<p>If youre a beginner, then youll need to invest lots of your time to understand <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-does-google-analytics-work-beginners-guide/\">how Google Analytics works</a>. Not only that you also need to spend money to hire a developer for configuring advanced metrics. </p>\n<p>But thankfully, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">MonsterInsights</a> plugin makes it super easy for WordPress users. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/monsterinsightsbestgapluginforwordpress.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights Best Google Analytics Plugin for WordPress\" width=\"620\" height=\"320\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-186638\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/monsterinsightsbestgapluginforwordpress.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/monsterinsightsbestgapluginforwordpress-300x155.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>It lets you configure form abandonment tracking and other important metrics in WordPress with just a few steps. </p>\n<p>To get started, you need to install and activate the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">MonsterInsights plugin</a> and then connect it with your Google Analytics account. For detailed instructions, see our step by step guide on how to <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-properly-setup-google-analytics-in-wordpress/\">install Google Analytics in WordPress with MonsterInsights</a>. </p>\n<p>After that, you need to install the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/addon/forms/\">MonsterInsights Forms addon</a> for tracking your forms. Go to <strong>MonsterInsights &raquo; Addons</strong> page from your dashboard and then install the Forms addon. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/installmiformsaddon.png\" alt=\"Install MonsterInsights Forms Addon\" width=\"620\" height=\"168\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213104\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/installmiformsaddon.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/installmiformsaddon-300x81.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Thats all! Now MonsterInsights will automatically start tracking your WordPress forms. </p>\n<p>If you want to reconfirm that, then you need to visit the <strong>MonsterInsights &raquo; Settings</strong> page and click on the Conversions tab. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/miformstrackingsettings.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights Forms Tracking Settings\" width=\"620\" height=\"406\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213105\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/miformstrackingsettings.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/miformstrackingsettings-300x196.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>As shown in the screenshot above, the plugin will automatically detect your form plugin, and enable forms tracking. It supports all the major <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\">WordPress form plugins</a> like <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a>, <a href=\"https://formidableforms.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Formidable Forms</a>, and more. </p>\n<p>After that, you may need to wait sometime to view your reports. It can take a few hours to 48 hours for Google Analytics to collect fresh data. </p>\n<h3>Viewing Your WordPress Form Tracking Stats</h3>\n<p>You can view your WordPress form tracking reports by going to <strong>MonsterInsights &raquo; Reports &raquo; Forms</strong> from your dashboard. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/monsterinsightsformsreport.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights Forms Tracking Reports\" width=\"620\" height=\"406\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213106\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/monsterinsightsformsreport.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/monsterinsightsformsreport-300x196.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>The MonsterInsights Forms report shows the total number of impressions, conversions, and conversion rate for each WordPress form. </p>\n<p>Now you can easily find out the number of people who abandoned your form. Wouldnt it be great if more people who viewed your form fill it out?</p>\n<p>You can view this report also in your Google Analytics account. Simply click on the View Full Forms Report button in your MonsterInsights forms report, and it will redirect you to the top events page in Google Analytics. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/gatopevents-wpformsreports.png\" alt=\"Google Analytics Top Events Report - Forms Conversions\" width=\"620\" height=\"327\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213107\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/gatopevents-wpformsreports.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/gatopevents-wpformsreports-300x158.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>As Google Analytics treats forms related actions as events, forms tracking reports are shown under the Events category. </p>\n<p>By default, you can see the stats for event action. You can click on the Event Label link to see the performance of your individual forms. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/eventlabelgatopevents.png\" alt=\"View Event Label for Google Analytics Events\" width=\"620\" height=\"275\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213108\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/eventlabelgatopevents.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/eventlabelgatopevents-300x133.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<h3>Recovering the Leads from the Abandoned Forms Using WPForms</h3>\n<p>Form abandonment is the real problem that you will miss your potential leads/ customers at the last point. But <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> users can now solve that problem and turn those abandoning users into loyal customers. </p>\n<p>WPForms is the most user-friendly as well as the most powerful WordPress form plugin in the market. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"WPForms Best WordPress Form Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-158461\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin-300x121.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>It allows you to easily <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-contact-form-in-wordpress-the-simple-way/\">create simple contact forms</a> to advanced forms like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-survey-in-wordpress/\">surveys</a>, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-an-order-form-in-wordpress-the-easy-way/\">order forms</a>, multi-page forms, and more in your WordPress blog. </p>\n<p>WPForms comes with an exclusive <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/form-abandonment-addon/\" target=\"_blank\">Form Abandonment addon</a> to help you recover leads from the abandoned forms. The addon saves partial entries and lets you follow up with the interested prospects. </p>\n<p>This feature is especially useful for support request forms, order forms, request quote forms, etc. For any reason, the users may have abandoned your form, but you can follow up and build new relationships with them. </p>\n<p>To use the addon, go to <strong>WPForms &raquo; Addons</strong> page and then install the Form Abandonment Addon. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/installformabandonmentaddonwpforms.png\" alt=\"Install Form Abandonment Addon WPForms Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"191\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213109\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/installformabandonmentaddonwpforms.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/installformabandonmentaddonwpforms-300x92.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>After that, you need to enable this option in your WordPress forms. If youve existing forms, then you need to edit them and enable this option. </p>\n<p>For example, well edit Billing / Order Form in our demo website. </p>\n<p>In your form editor screen, click on the Settings menu. After that, click the Form Abandonment option and check the box next to Enable form abandonment lead capture. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/enableformabandonmentleadcapturewpforms.png\" alt=\"Enable Form Abandonment Lead Capture in WPForms\" width=\"620\" height=\"278\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213110\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/enableformabandonmentleadcapturewpforms.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/enableformabandonmentleadcapturewpforms-300x135.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Thats all! Now WPForms will record the entries for the abandoned forms and lets you optimize them. </p>\n<p>Like all the other entries, you can find the abandoned form entries as well in the Entries menu. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/entry-status-for-abandoned-and-completed-forms.png\" alt=\"Entry Status of Abandoned and Completed Forms\" width=\"518\" height=\"410\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213111\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/entry-status-for-abandoned-and-completed-forms.png 518w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/entry-status-for-abandoned-and-completed-forms-300x237.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 518px) 100vw, 518px\" /></p>\n<p>Now you can contact these users and offer them the products they may be interested in. </p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to learn how to track form abandonment in WordPress  the easy way. And also to learn to how to recover leads from the abandoned forms using WPForms. </p>\n<p>You may also want to see our step by step guide on how to <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-add-google-analytics-to-amp-pages-on-wordpress/\">track your AMP traffic using Google Analytics</a>. </p>\n<p>And dont forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more helpful Google Analytics tips.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-track-form-abandonment-in-wordpress/\">How to Track Form Abandonment in WordPress (The Easy Way)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-track-form-abandonment-in-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"35+ Best WordPress Plugins 2019 (Grow Your Website FASTER!)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:169:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 27 Jun 2019 14:10:21 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Tools\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"WordPress Plugins free\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"best plugins for WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"best WordPress plugins and tools\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"WordPress marketing tools\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"wordpress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/?p=162098\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:634:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress plugins 2019 to grow your website fast? With over 55,000 official free plugins and almost the same number of premium plugins, you&#8217;ve plenty of tools to optimize your website in WordPress. However, it&#8217;s quite a tricky job to pick the best plugins from such an extensive collection. But [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers/\">35+ Best WordPress Plugins 2019 (Grow Your Website FASTER!)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73159:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress plugins 2019 to grow your website fast? </p>\n<p>With over 55,000 official free plugins and almost the same number of premium plugins, you&#8217;ve plenty of tools to optimize your website in WordPress. </p>\n<p>However, it&#8217;s quite a tricky job to pick the best plugins from such an extensive collection. But don&#8217;t worry, we&#8217;re here to help you!</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share with you 35+ best WordPress plugins and tools to grow your website or blog faster in 2019. </p>\n<h3>Best WordPress Plugins for 2019 &#8211; Quick Overview</h3>\n<p>Lets get started with a quick overview of the best WordPress plugins on our list. </p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"#monsterinsights\">MonsterInsights</a> &#8211; Best WordPress Google Analytics Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#optinmonster\">OptinMonster</a> &#8211; Best WordPress Popup Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#wpforms\">WPForms</a> &#8211; Most Beginner-friendly WordPress Form Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#seedprod\">SeedProd</a> &#8211; Best WordPress Coming Soon Page Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#yoastseo\">Yoast SEO</a> &#8211; Most Popular WordPress SEO Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#sucuri\">Sucuri</a> &#8211; Top WordPress Security Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#backupbuddy\">BackupBuddy</a> &#8211; Most Powerful WordPress Backup Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#memberpress\">MemberPress</a> &#8211; Best WordPress Membership Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#learndash\">LearnDash</a> &#8211; Best LMS Plugin for WordPress</li>\n<li><a href=\"#affiliateroyale\">Affiliate Royale</a> &#8211; Best WordPress Affiliate Program Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#prettylinks\">Pretty Links</a> &#8211; Best WordPress Affiliate Marketing Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#livechat\">LiveChat</a> &#8211; Best Live Chat Software for WordPress</li>\n<li><a href=\"#sharedcounts\">Shared Counts</a> &#8211; Best WordPress Social Media Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#trustpulse\">TrustPulse</a> &#8211; Best WordPress Social Proof Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#wpmailsmtp\">WP Mail SMTP</a> &#8211; Best SMTP and PHP Mailer Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#beaverbuilder\">Beaver Builder</a> &#8211; Most Powerful WordPress Page Builder</li>\n<li><a href=\"#enviragallery\">Envira Gallery</a> &#8211; Best WordPress Gallery Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#soliloquy\">Soliloquy</a> &#8211; Best WordPress Slider Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#csshero\">CSS Hero</a> &#8211; Powerful WordPress Theme Editor Tool</li>\n<li><a href=\"#smartslider3\">Smart Slider 3</a> &#8211; Responsive WordPress Slider Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#woocommerce\">WooCommerce</a> &#8211; Most Popular eCommerce Plugin for WordPress</li>\n<li><a href=\"#w3totalcache\">W3 Total Cache</a> &#8211; Best WordPress Caching Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#wpsmush\">WP Smush</a> &#8211; Powerful Image Compression Tool for WordPress</li>\n<li><a href=\"#birchpress\">BirchPress</a> &#8211; Best WordPress Appointment Booking Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#eventscalendar\">The Events Calendar</a> &#8211; Top WordPress Event Management Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#adsanity\">AdSanity</a> &#8211; Best Ad Management Plugin for WordPress</li>\n<li><a href=\"#tablepress\">TablePress</a> &#8211; Most Popular WordPress Table Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#insertheadersfooters\">Insert Headers and Footers</a> &#8211; Best Code Inserter Plugin for WordPress</li>\n<li><a href=\"#googlexmlsitemaps\">Google XML Sitemaps</a> &#8211; Popular XML Sitemaps Plugin for WordPress</li>\n<li><a href=\"#brokenlinkchecker\">Broken Link Checker</a> &#8211; Useful WordPress SEO Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#reviveoldposts\">Revive Old Posts</a> &#8211; Must-have WordPress Social Media Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#inlinerelatedposts\">Inline Related Posts</a> &#8211; Amazing Content Optimization Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#quickeasyfaqs\">Quick and Easy FAQs</a> &#8211; Best FAQ Plugin for WordPress</li>\n<li><a href=\"#easygooglefonts\">Easy Google Fonts</a> &#8211; Best WordPress Google Fonts Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#loginlockdown\">Login Lockdown</a> &#8211; Powerful WordPress Login Protection Plugin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#duplicator\">Duplicator</a> &#8211; Best WordPress Migration Plugin</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> After the plugins, we&#8217;ve also included <strong>pro tips for choosing the best WordPress plugin</strong> at the end. Read the full article to find them!</p>\n<p>Now, lets take a look at the best WordPress plugins with a quick description and review for each.</p>\n<h3 id=\"monsterinsights\"><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">1. MonsterInsights &#8211; Best WordPress Google Analytics Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-157422\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-best-ga-plugin-for-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"monsterinsights-best-ga-plugin-for-wordpress\" width=\"620\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-best-ga-plugin-for-wordpress.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-best-ga-plugin-for-wordpress-300x121.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a><br />\nGoogle Analytics is one of the most popular marketing tools widely-used by professionals as well as beginners. It helps you understand exactly how users find and use your website so you can make informed marketing decisions.</p>\n<p>In WordPress, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">MonsterInsights</a> helps you use Google Analytics like a pro and grow your business with confidence. It allows you to <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-properly-setup-google-analytics-in-wordpress/\">set up Google Analytics in WordPress</a> easily and provides you with detailed reports on your website traffic and their interactions with your site.</p>\n<p>With MonsterInsights, you can set up advanced tracking like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/addon/ecommerce/\">eCommerce</a>, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/addon/forms/\">forms</a>, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/addon/ads/\">ads</a>, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/addon/dimensions/\">custom dimensions</a>, etc. with ease. And, you can see all the analytics reports within your WordPress dashboard without having to navigate away from your site.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts from $99.50 / year. (Free version is also available.)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/pricing/\">Get started with MonsterInsights today!</a></p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\">Want to know how we choose the best plugins? We&#8217;ll reveal that at last. Read on!</div>\n<h3 id=\"optinmonster\"><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">2. OptinMonster &#8211; Best WordPress Popup Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155241\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software.jpg\" alt=\"optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software\" width=\"560\" height=\"260\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software-300x139.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">OptinMonster</a> is the best lead generation software available on the market. It helps you to convert your website traffic into leads and boost your conversions and sales.</p>\n<p>With OptinMonster, you can create beautiful email optin forms and display them strategically on your site. You can create different types of campaigns including lightbox popups, inline forms, sidebar forms, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-add-a-countdown-timer-in-wordpress/\">countdown timers</a>, etc. and use smart triggers to display them on your site to the right people.</p>\n<p>OptinMonsters signature <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/exit-intent/\">Exit-Intent technology</a> helps you convert abandoning visitors into subscribers and customers. Other triggers, like scroll trigger, <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/monsterlinks/\">MonsterLinks 2-step optins</a>, InactivitySensor, etc. are also very effective. OptinMonster is nothing less than a phenomenal email marketing tool.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts from $9 / month. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get started with OptinMonster today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"wpforms\"><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">3. WPForms &#8211; Best Form Builder Plugin for WordPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-158461\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin-300x121.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a><br />\nOne of the most common strategies used by successful marketers is creating connections with customers. And, <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WPForms</a> is the right tool for that. </p>\n<p>Its a powerful WordPress forms plugin that allows you to <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-contact-form-in-wordpress-the-simple-way/\">create simple contact forms</a> as well as advanced forms like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-an-order-form-in-wordpress-the-easy-way/\">order forms</a>, payment forms, donation forms, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-survey-in-wordpress/\">survey forms</a>, and polls. It&#8217;s one of the most popular WordPress plugins in the world. </p>\n<p>WPForms is a user-friendly and straightforward plugin anyone can use without touching any code. You can find pre-built form templates to quickly start making forms. Plus, it features an intuitive drag and drop form builder.</p>\n<p>Then, you can embed the forms easily in blog posts, pages, sidebar widgets, footer areas, etc. quickly. WPForms is a great form builder plugin and marketing tool for WordPress.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts from $39.50 / year. (Free version is also available.)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get started with WPForms today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"seedprod\"><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\">4. SeedProd</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/seedprod-coming-soon-page-wordpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"SeedProd Best Coming Soon and Maintenance Mode WordPress Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"280\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-157623\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/seedprod-coming-soon-page-wordpress-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/seedprod-coming-soon-page-wordpress-plugin-300x135.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If youre planning for a big launch of your new website, then SeedProd is the plugin you need to start with. It allows you to create a professional coming soon page in a matter of minutes, and start an online buzz for your new site.  </p>\n<p>SeedProd is the #1 coming soon page and maintenance mode plugin for WordPress. It comes with over 50 beautiful themes, 500,000 free background images, and 750 Google fonts to let you create a stunning coming soon page. </p>\n<p>The plugin has integration with the best <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-email-newsletter-tools-compared-pros-and-cons/\">email newsletter tools</a> like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/convertkit/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">ConvertKit</a>, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/mailchimp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">MailChimp</a> to let you <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/why-collect-emails-benefits-of-building-an-email-list/\">collect emails</a>. It also has a password-protect feature to allow your clients special access. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts from $37 / year. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get started with SeedProd today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"yoastseo\"><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">5. Yoast SEO &#8211; Best WordPress SEO Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-154146\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoast-seo-best-free-wordpress-seo-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"yoast-seo-best-free-wordpress-seo-plugin\" width=\"560\" height=\"182\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoast-seo-best-free-wordpress-seo-plugin.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoast-seo-best-free-wordpress-seo-plugin-300x98.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a><br />\nSEO is yet another important aspect of digital marketing. As Google gets the most internet traffic, you can get the most organic traffic if your site gets better ranking in search results.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Yoast SEO</a> is the best WordPress SEO plugin available. It helps you to make your entire website&#8217;s content SEO-friendly. It analyses your blog content and provides an SEO score, and also provides you with suggestions on how to make improvements.</p>\n<p>Furthermore, it takes care of the technical stuff like robots.txt, permalink URLs, sitemaps, etc. and is continuously updated with Googles latest algorithms.</p>\n<p>Yoast SEO is one of the most downloaded WordPress plugins on the internet. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts from $89 / year. (Free version is also available.)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Yoast SEO today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"sucuri\"><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/sucuri/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">6. Sucuri &#8211; Best WordPress Security Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/sucuri/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155274\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sucuri-wordpress-security.jpg\" alt=\"sucuri-wordpress-se