s-and-footers-plugin-300x98.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/insert-headers-and-footers/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Insert Headers and Footers</a> is a cool WordPress plugin for business owners with few-to-no coding skills because it helps you to add code to your themes header or footer area easily without actually having to learn how to code.</p>\n<p>Sometimes, you may need to add codes such as Google Analytics&#8217; tracking code, meta verification, custom CSS, etc. to your themes header or footer area. But, to edit your themes header.php and footer.php file, you&#8217;d need to have excellent coding skills. Plus, it can be risky to make changes to these files.</p>\n<p>Insert Headers and Footers plugin saves you from all that. Another benefit of using this plugin is that your Google Analytics tracking code will not be lost, even if you change your theme.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/insert-headers-and-footers/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get started with Insert Headers and Footers today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"googlexmlsitemaps\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-sitemap-generator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">29. Google XML Sitemaps &#8211; Pupular XML Sitemaps Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-sitemap-generator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-162125\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/google-xml-sitemaps-wordpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"google-xml-sitemaps-wordpress-plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"198\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/google-xml-sitemaps-wordpress-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/google-xml-sitemaps-wordpress-plugin-300x96.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-sitemap-generator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Google XML Sitemaps</a> is one of the most loved free WordPress plugins in the official WordPress plugin repository. Its a great <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-seo-plugins-and-tools/\">WordPress SEO plugin</a> that helps to improve SEO by creating XML sitemaps.</p>\n<p>XML sitemaps help search engines better index your site as they allow the search engine crawlers to see the complete structure of your site. Thus, this helps your website get better rankings in search results.</p>\n<p>Also, it notifies all the major search engines like Google, Bing, Yahoo, Ask.com, etc. each time you publish new content. Its simple and easy to use.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-sitemap-generator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Google XML Sitemaps today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"brokenlinkchecker\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/broken-link-checker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">30. Broken Link Checker &#8211; Must-have WordPress Plugin for SEO</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/broken-link-checker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-162130\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/broken-link-checker-wordpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"broken-link-checker-wordpress-plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"198\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/broken-link-checker-wordpress-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/broken-link-checker-wordpress-plugin-300x96.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/broken-link-checker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Broken Link Checker</a> is one of the most user-friendly WordPress plugins ever made. </p>\n<p>Just as its name says, Broken Link Checker is a plugin that monitors your site for broken links and missing images. If it detects any broken links or missing images, it immediately notifies you so you can instantly fix them.</p>\n<p>Furthermore, it can make broken links display differently in posts and prevent search engines from following such links. Thus, the plugin saves you from negative SEO rankings.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/broken-link-checker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Broken Link Checker today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"reviveoldposts\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">31. Revive Old Posts &#8211; Must-have Social Media Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-162113\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revive-old-post-wordpress-p.jpg\" alt=\"revive-old-post-wordpress-p\" width=\"620\" height=\"198\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revive-old-post-wordpress-p.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revive-old-post-wordpress-p-300x96.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a><br />\nSocial media marketing is a comparatively new component in the digital marketing world, but it&#8217;s a very effective one. Its a way of engaging the huge social media audience with your marketing content.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Revive Old Posts</a> is an incredible plugin for social media marketing and <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-content-marketing-plugins-and-tools-for-wordpress/\">content marketing</a>. The plugin helps you engage people on social media with your old WordPress posts. You can automatically share your old WordPress articles using this plugin and drive traffic to your site.</p>\n<p>The plugin allows you to choose the time between posts and the number of posts to share to make it organized. Plus, you can use hashtags to focus on topics.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Revive Old Posts today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"inlinerelatedposts\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/intelly-related-posts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">32. Inline Related Posts &#8211; Cool Content Optimization Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/intelly-related-posts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-162129\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/inline-related-posts-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"inline-related-posts-plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"198\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/inline-related-posts-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/inline-related-posts-plugin-300x96.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/intelly-related-posts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Inline Related Posts</a> plugin helps you enhance user engagement on your WordPress posts by displaying related content inside your articles. Most websites show related content after the end of articles due to which users need to scroll down the whole article to see the related content. But people can exit your post anywhere in-between if they dont find it useful.</p>\n<p>So, the plugin can help you to keep your visitors on site by displaying related posts. If they see the relevant content more useful, they can switch to that post instead of leaving your site. This technique is especially helpful for long articles.</p>\n<p>This is a very simple-yet-interesting marketing strategy which can improve user engagement on your WordPress blogs.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/intelly-related-posts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Inline Related Posts today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"quickeasyfaqs\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-and-easy-faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">33. Quick and Easy FAQs &#8211; Best FAQ Management Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-and-easy-faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-162131\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quick-and-easy-faqs-wordpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"quick-and-easy-faqs-wordpress-plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"198\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quick-and-easy-faqs-wordpress-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quick-and-easy-faqs-wordpress-plugin-300x96.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Frequently asked questions (FAQs) are widely used on websites to answer common questions. By adding the FAQ section on your site, you can solve several queries your site visitors want to ask without having to manually reply to each visitor.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-and-easy-faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Quick and Easy FAQs</a> is a free WordPress plugin that makes it easy to create beautiful FAQs in WordPress. You can display the FAQs in different styles like simple list style, toggle style, filterable toggle, etc.</p>\n<p>In short, this plugin helps you to improve communication and increase your conversions.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-and-easy-faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Quick and Easy FAQs today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"easygooglefonts\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-google-fonts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">34. Easy Google Fonts &#8211; Best Googe Fonts WordPress Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-google-fonts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-154158\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/easy-google-fonts-free-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"easy-google-fonts-free-plugin\" width=\"560\" height=\"182\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/easy-google-fonts-free-plugin.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/easy-google-fonts-free-plugin-300x98.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Typography is one of the significant aspects of good design. If your theme doesnt have cool fonts, your website design may not be eye-catching enough to maintain your visitors&#8217; interests.</p>\n<p>However, you can use the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-google-fonts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Easy Google Fonts</a> plugin and solve this problem easily. Its a free plugin that lets you use 600+ Google fonts on your WordPress site. Using this plugin is easy; no coding is required. Even a beginner can effortlessly configure the plugin and add beautiful fonts in WordPress.</p>\n<p>The plugin uses a live customizer so that you can preview fonts in real-time as you make changes.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-google-fonts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Easy Google Fonts today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"loginlockdown\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/login-lockdown/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">35. Login Lockdown &#8211; Useful WordPress Security Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/login-lockdown/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-154159\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/login-lockdown-free-wp-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"login-lockdown-free-wp-plugin\" width=\"560\" height=\"182\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/login-lockdown-free-wp-plugin.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/login-lockdown-free-wp-plugin-300x98.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Although you set a strong username and password to access your WordPress dashboard, it can sometimes fall prey to brute force password discovery. So, youll need to use the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/login-lockdown/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Login Lockdown</a> plugin to protect your site from such attacks.</p>\n<p>It records the IP address and timestamp for every failed login attempt. If it detects more than a set number of failed login attempts, it disables the login function for that user for a specified period.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s an essential WordPress plugin to keep your website secure. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/login-lockdown/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Login Lockdown today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"duplicator\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/duplicator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">36. Duplicator &#8211; Best WordPress Migration Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/duplicator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-154161\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/duplicator-free-wordpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"duplicator-free-wordpress-plugin\" width=\"560\" height=\"182\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/duplicator-free-wordpress-plugin.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/duplicator-free-wordpress-plugin-300x98.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/duplicator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Duplicator</a>, as its name suggests, helps you to duplicate your website data. Its useful when you need to move your website data from one location to another, like moving to a new host. This is also helpful for creating site backups.</p>\n<p>Using Duplicator, you can clone the live site data and install it on localhost for moving your site. Then, with the help of localhost data, you can move your site to a new web host without downtime.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/duplicator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Duplicator today!</a></p>\n<p>Before wrapping it up, here&#8217;s what we have promised above! </p>\n<h3 id=\"chooseplugin\">How to Choose the Best WordPress Plugin for Your Website?</h3>\n<p>WordPress plugins let you add extra functionality to improve your website design, marketing, and a variety of other aspects related to growth. </p>\n<p>However, WordPress beginners cannot find the best plugins because they don&#8217;t know how to choose them. Here&#8217;re some simple tips you can use to find the best WordPress plugins. </p>\n<p><strong>1. User Reviews and Ratings</strong></p>\n<p>User reviews and ratings give you plenty of idea on how the plugin works in reality. And, you can rely on them because they&#8217;re the actual experiences of the plugin users. </p>\n<p>You can find WordPress plugin reviews and ratings in the sidebar area on the official WordPress.org plugin pages. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wppluginreviews.png\" alt=\"WordPress Plugins Review to Choose the Best WordPress Plugins\" width=\"620\" height=\"365\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208799\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wppluginreviews.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wppluginreviews-300x177.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>You can view full reviews by clicking on the &#8216;See all&#8217; link in the Rating section.  </p>\n<p>For example, our plugin <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-analytics-for-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\">MonsterInsights</a> has received 808 five-star ratings out of 1035 total reviews. The best part is that all the recent reviews are five-star ratings. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/miratingsandreviews.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights Plugin Reviews and Ratings\" width=\"620\" height=\"443\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208803\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/miratingsandreviews.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/miratingsandreviews-300x214.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2. Customer Support</strong></p>\n<p>Customer support is another crucial thing to consider while choosing the best plugins for WordPress. You need a plugin that provides you instant support whenever you need it. </p>\n<p>For official WordPress plugins, you can view the support forum in WordPress.org. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/misupportforum.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights Support Forum\" width=\"620\" height=\"355\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208805\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/misupportforum.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/misupportforum-300x172.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>For example, the MonsterInsights support forum has all the questions already solved (the tick mark).</p>\n<p><strong>3. Plugin Screenshots</strong></p>\n<p>Plugin screenshots let you see how the plugin interface looks in the backend and frontend. You need a simple interface to work efficiently. </p>\n<p>You can find the plugin screenshots in the WordPress.org Plugin pages. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mipluginscreenshots.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights Plugin Screenshots\" width=\"620\" height=\"447\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208808\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mipluginscreenshots.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mipluginscreenshots-300x216.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>That&#8217;s it! </p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress plugins and tools to grow your business website fast in 2019. You may also want to check out our list of <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-hosting-services/\">best WordPress hosting services 2019</a>.</p>\n<p>Also, dont forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more useful WordPress tutorials.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers/\">35+ Best WordPress Plugins 2019 (Grow Your Website FASTER!)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"10 Best WordPress Popup Plugins for 2019 (Review + Guide)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:133:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-popup-plugins/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=best-wordpress-popup-plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-popup-plugins/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 24 Jun 2019 18:33:28 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Tools\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"WordPress popup\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"popup plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"WordPress popup plugin free\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"popup templates\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/?p=211584\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:619:\"<p>Are you looking to add popups on your WordPress site? Want to know which is the best WordPress popup plugin? Choosing the right popup builder is crucial for making well-designed popups, which can convert your users into subscribers/customers/loyal fans. In this article, well share with you 10 best WordPress popup plugins you can use to [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-popup-plugins/\">10 Best WordPress Popup Plugins for 2019 (Review + Guide)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21387:\"<p>Are you looking to add popups on your WordPress site? Want to know which is the best WordPress popup plugin? </p>\n<p>Choosing the right popup builder is crucial for making well-designed popups, which can convert your users into subscribers/customers/loyal fans.  </p>\n<p>In this article, well share with you 10 best WordPress popup plugins you can use to create popups in 2019. </p>\n<h3>How to Choose the Best WordPress Popup Plugin?</h3>\n<p>Popups can maximize your website conversions by displaying attractive offers at the appropriate time. You can learn more by reading some <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/category/case-studies/\" target=\"_blank\">case studies about OptinMonster users</a>. </p>\n<p>However, they can be annoying sometimes. If your popups look unattractive and appear at inappropriate times, then they can rather ruin user experience on your website. </p>\n<p>Thats why you need a proper popup plugin to create attractive popups. </p>\n<p>Herere some points to consider while selecting the best popup plugin for your WordPress site.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Look for the popup templates offered by the plugin.</li>\n<li>Check out campaign types the plugin lets you create.</li>\n<li>Find out the supported triggers for popups.</li>\n<li>You need <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-email-newsletter-tools-compared-pros-and-cons/\">email marketing</a> integration for maximum conversions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>With that said, lets take a look at our selection of best popup plugins for WordPress. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">1. OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinmonster-bestpopupandleadgenerationtool.png\" alt=\"OptinMonster Best Popup and Lead Generation Tool\" width=\"620\" height=\"367\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-211601\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinmonster-bestpopupandleadgenerationtool.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinmonster-bestpopupandleadgenerationtool-300x178.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">OptinMonster</a> is the most powerful popup plugin in the market. It is a SaaS (software as a service) platform that you can easily integrate with WordPress, WooCommerce, Shopify, and many different website and <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-email-newsletter-tools-compared-pros-and-cons/\">email marketing services</a>. </p>\n<p>Using OptinMonster, you can easily create visually stunning popups and use them to <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/why-collect-emails-benefits-of-building-an-email-list/\">collect emails</a>, promote your product sales, and more. </p>\n<p>It allows you to create different types of popup campaigns: lightbox popup, fullscreen welcome mat, slide-in scroll box, floating bar, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-add-a-countdown-timer-in-wordpress/\">countdown timer</a>, content locker, notification bars etc.  </p>\n<p>You can use smart triggers like scroll-trigger, InactivitySensor, Timed Display Control, 2-Step Yes / No Optins, etc. to display popups in the appropriate time. Above all, its signature <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/exit-intent/\" target\"_blank\">Exit-Intent technology</a> lets you show a targeted campaign at the exact moment your visitors are about to leave and convert abandoning visitors into subscribers. </p>\n<p>Moreover, it has powerful features like geo-location targeting, device-based targeting, page level targeting etc. to let you create targeted popup campaigns. Trusted by more than 700,000 websites, OptinMonster is the #1 choice for creating popups and optin forms in WordPress. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starting from $9 / month for Basic plan. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get started with OptinMonster today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/sumome/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Sumo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/sumome/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sumo.png\" alt=\"Sumo Email List Building Tool\" width=\"620\" height=\"367\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-211603\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sumo.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sumo-300x178.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Sumo is yet another powerful tool for creating popups on your website. Similar to OptinMonster, its also a standalone software which you can integrate with your WordPress site and add popups.</p>\n<p>Sumo comes with a bundle of well-crafted email optin templates ready for use. You can choose one, customize with different elements like fonts, colors, add suitable triggers, and publish on your website. </p>\n<p>It lets you display popups based on clicks, timers, scrolls, and exit-intent. However, it doesnt have 2-Step Yes / No optins and content locking form options. </p>\n<p>One advantage of using Sumo is that you can find a free version of it. However, it comes with limited features and functionalities. Used by over 500,000 websites, Sumo is a cool alternative for OptinMonster.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free or $39 / month for Pro plan. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/sumome/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Sumo today!</a> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bloom/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Bloom</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bloom/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/bloompopuppluginwp.png\" alt=\"Bloom WordPress Popup and Optin Plugjn\" width=\"620\" height=\"316\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-211604\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/bloompopuppluginwp.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/bloompopuppluginwp-300x153.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Unlike OptinMonster and Sumo, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bloom/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bloom</a> is a WordPress plugin. Created by Elegant Themes, it is one of the most widely used popup plugins in the market. </p>\n<p>Bloom comes with more than 100 amazing templates to let you create email optin forms on your WordPress site. </p>\n<p>You can choose from 6 different display types: automatic optin popup, optin fly-ins, inline optin forms, below content optin forms, widget area optin forms, and optin to unlock the content. </p>\n<p>It lets you trigger popups at the timed delay, after readers reach the bottom of the post, after commenting, after purchasing, and after inactivity. However, it misses out the most effective triggers like exit-intent, floating bars, geo-location targeting, etc. </p>\n<p>You can get access to Bloom plugin only by purchasing to one of the Elegant Themes membership plans. So if youve already bought their membership, then you can use Bloom without extra payment. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: $89 / year for Yearly Access Plan. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bloom/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Bloom today!</a> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/thriveleads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Thrive Leads</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/thriveleads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/thriveleadsplugin.png\" alt=\"Thrive Leads List Building and Popup WordPress Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"322\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-211605\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/thriveleadsplugin.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/thriveleadsplugin-300x156.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/thriveleads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Thrive Leads</a> is a WordPress popup and list building tool by Thrive Themes. It is also a powerful solution with tons of advanced features. </p>\n<p>Similar to OptinMonster, it includes advanced optin types like 2-Step Yes / No optins, content locking, screen filler overlay, sticky ribbon, and more. However, it has limited targeting and trigger options. </p>\n<p>It supports timed popup display, scroll trigger, exit-intent, and WordPress category and tag targeting. But it misses out powerful triggers like geo-location targeting, InactivitySeonsor, etc. </p>\n<p>Thrive Leads also includes A/B testing to help you choose the best possible optin form. You can also find stats and reports and view the performance of your popups. </p>\n<p>With all these excellent features, Thrive Leads is an excellent alternative to Bloom plugin.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: $67 / year for 1 License. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/thriveleads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Thrive Leads today!</a> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.optimonk.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. OptiMonk</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.optimonk.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optimonk.png\" alt=\"OptiMonk Optin and Popup Form Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"303\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-211607\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optimonk.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optimonk-300x147.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>OptiMonk is yet another SaaS platform for creating popups on your website. It works well with WordPress as well as Shopify, BigCommerce, Magento, and other platforms. </p>\n<p>OptiMonk lets you create optin forms for various purposes like capturing email subscribers, reducing cart abandonment, promoting special offers, collecting feedback, and more. </p>\n<p>It includes smart features to show the right message to the right people at the right moment. It allows you to check visitor background, and use page-level targeting and time-based targeting for better results. </p>\n<p>Using OptiMonk, you can use triggers like timed display, scroll and click monitoring, and exit-intent detection. However, it lacks the cool features like URL parameter targeting, WordPress category and tag targeting, and more. </p>\n<p>Bundled with 30+ beautiful templates, OptiMonk is an excellent alternative for Sumo lead generation tool discussed above. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free or $29 / month for Essential plan. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.optimonk.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with OptiMonk today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/popup-maker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Popup Maker</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/popup-maker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/popupmakerwpplugin.png\" alt=\"Popup Maker Free WordPress Poup Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"207\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-211608\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/popupmakerwpplugin.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/popupmakerwpplugin-300x100.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Popup Maker is the best free WordPress popup plugin available in the market. The plugin is actively installed on more than 300,000 websites. Plus, it has received 4.9 out of 5 average ratings from its users on WordPress.org. </p>\n<p>The plugin lets you create optin popups, slide-ins, modal forms, and also the EU cookie notices. You can set popup triggers on timed delay and click-based triggers on the navigation to menu items, buttons, sidebars, etc. </p>\n<p>It lacks many advanced targeting and trigger options as offered in OptinMonster and other plugins above. However, you can get Exit-intent feature by purchasing their paid extension plugin. </p>\n<p>It supports all the major <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\">WordPress form plugins</a> like <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a>, and email newsletter tools like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/mailchimp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">MailChimp</a> and <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/aweber/\" target=\"_blank\" re=\"nofollow\">AWeber</a>. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/popup-maker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Popup Maker today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/popup-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Popup Builder</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/popup-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/popupbuilderfreewpplugin.png\" alt=\"Popup Builder Free Plugin for WordPress Popups\" width=\"620\" height=\"207\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-211609\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/popupbuilderfreewpplugin.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/popupbuilderfreewpplugin-300x100.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Popup Builder is yet another WordPress popup plugin available for free. It has over 100,000 active installs and 4.8 out 5 stars average rating on WordPress.org. </p>\n<p>The plugin helps you to create and manage appealing promotion modal popups on your WordPress website. You can show offers, discounts, and other kinds of promotional content and increase your conversion rate. </p>\n<p>The plugin lets you choose a popup display location and a theme from many options available. You can set popup triggers on page scrolling, on click, on mouse hover, etc. with this free plugin. </p>\n<p>If you want to use its advanced features, then youll need to buy its premium version. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/popup-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Popup Builder today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/popups/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Popups</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/popups/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/poups.png\" alt=\"Popups Simple WordPress popup plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"301\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214709\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/poups.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/poups-300x146.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/popups/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Popups</a> is a free simple WordPress popup plugin you can use to boost your site conversion rates. It allows you to create different types of popups with the call to action buttons, social icons, and email subscription forms. </p>\n<p>You can display your popups in 5 different locations using an appropriate trigger. It has multiple popup triggers like after X seconds, after scrolling % of the page, after scrolling X pixels, etc. </p>\n<p>Also, therere multiple display filters. You can choose to show the popup on specific pages, posts, etc. Also, it lets you filter users from search engines, users that never commented, that arrived from another page on your site, etc. </p>\n<p>It works well with <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\">contact form plugins</a> and email marketing services like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/mailchimp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">MailChimp</a>. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/popups/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Popups plugin today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/elementor-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Elementor Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/elementor-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/elementorpopupbuilder.png\" alt=\"Elementor Popup Builder for WordPress\" width=\"620\" height=\"285\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214710\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/elementorpopupbuilder.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/elementorpopupbuilder-300x138.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Elementor Pro is one of the widely used <a href=https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-drag-and-drop-wordpress-page-builders/>drag and drop page builder plugins</a> for WordPress. You can use it for building stunning landing pages on your website. </p>\n<p>The plugin now includes a powerful popup builder tool as well. If youre already using Elementor Pro on your website, then you can get popups without paying extra money.</p>\n<p>Using Elementor Popup Builder, you can create different types of popups including email subscriptions, login forms, promotions and sale banners, welcome mat, etc. You can use different styles like a fly in, full screen, help bar, bottom bar, slide in, and more.   </p>\n<p>Therere 100+ stylish popup templates available to let you make popups quickly. You can also use 100+ Elementor content widgets and create unlimited popups for your website. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: $49 / year for Personal plan (1 Site)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/elementor-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Elementor Pro Popup Builder today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/icegram/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. Icegram</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/icegram/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/icegram.png\" alt=\"Icegram free Poup Builder Plugin WordPress\" width=\"620\" height=\"329\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214711\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/icegram.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/icegram-300x159.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Last but not the list, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/icegram/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Icegram</a> is an easy to use popup form plugin for WordPress. It allows you to make beautiful optins and call to actions on your website and convert your visitors to subscribers and customers. </p>\n<p>Using Icegram, you can use mainly 4 types of popup styles: lightbox popups, header and footer action bars, toast notifications, and slide in messengers. </p>\n<p>You can choose to display the popups on specific pages, categories, posts, and on different locations like the top, middle, bottom, left, right, or center of the pages. </p>\n<p>You can connect your popup forms with email newsletter tools like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Constant Contact</a>, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/aweber/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AWeber</a>, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/getresponse/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">GetResponse</a>, and grow your email list. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/icegram/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Icegram today!</a></p>\n<h3>Which is the Best Popup Plugin for WordPress?</h3>\n<p>After reviewing the most popular popup plugins available, we believe that <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">OptinMonster</a> is the best popup tool you can use. </p>\n<p>It includes advanced triggers and targeting options like Exit-Intent technology, mobile triggers, geo-site targeting, etc. And, it offers a user-friendly and straightforward drag and drop interface for creating optins. </p>\n<p>If you want to find out how OptinMonster tops the list, you can see this head to head <a href= https://optinmonster.com/compare/ target=_blank>comparison table between OptinMonster and its alternatives</a>. </p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to find the best WordPress popup plugin for your website. You may also want to see our handpicked list of <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers/\">best WordPress plugins</a> to grow your site faster. </p>\n<p>And dont forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more helpful Google Analytics tips.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-popup-plugins/\">10 Best WordPress Popup Plugins for 2019 (Review + Guide)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-popup-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"7 Best WordPress Plugins &amp; Tools to Add Social Proof and Boost Your Sales [2019]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:187:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-social-proof-wordpress-plugins-to-boost-your-sales/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=best-social-proof-wordpress-plugins-to-boost-your-sales\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:96:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-social-proof-wordpress-plugins-to-boost-your-sales/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 20 Jun 2019 14:32:51 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Tools\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"social proof\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"fomo wordpress plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"social proof examples\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/?p=208732\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:661:\"<p>Are you looking for the best social proof WordPress plugins for your website? Social proof is any content which shows that your services are socially approved, trusted, and used by people. Using social proof on your website helps to increase trust for your company and boosts your sales. Thats why big brands like Amazon and [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-social-proof-wordpress-plugins-to-boost-your-sales/\">7 Best WordPress Plugins &#038; Tools to Add Social Proof and Boost Your Sales [2019]</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16195:\"<p>Are you looking for the best social proof WordPress plugins for your website? Social proof is any content which shows that your services are socially approved, trusted, and used by people. </p>\n<p>Using social proof on your website helps to increase trust for your company and boosts your sales. Thats why big brands like Amazon and many others are using social proof on their site. </p>\n<p>In this article, well share with you 7 best social proof WordPress plugins 2019 to boost your sales. </p>\n<h3>What is Social Proof? + Social Proof Examples</h3>\n<p>Social proof is a psychological phenomenon where people rely on the actions of others to decide what is right and what is wrong. </p>\n<p>It is a type of conformity that people use at ambiguous times  they observe what others are doing and copy the same behavior. It assumes that people perceive group behavior as appropriate behavior. </p>\n<p>Marketers have long been using this principle as a tactic to gain the trust of new consumers. </p>\n<p>Some of the most popular social proof examples in use are testimonials, customer reviews, celebrity brand endorsements, certifications, and various stats.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/customertestimonials.png\" alt=\"Customer Testimonials as Social Proof\" width=\"620\" height=\"266\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210796\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/customertestimonials.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/customertestimonials-300x129.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Here is a simple example: Users come to your website and think of buying your product, but they cannot decide because they dont trust you. But if you have added a testimonial from a known industry expert next to the purchase button, then theyre more likely to trust and buy your product. </p>\n<p>With that said, lets take a look at the best WordPress social proof plugins you can use to grow your sales and revenue. </p>\n<h3>Best Social Proof Marketing Plugins for WordPress (2019)</h3>\n<h3><a href=\"https://trustpulse.com/\" target=\"_blank\">1. TrustPulse</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://trustpulse.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/trustpulsebestsocialproofapp.png\" alt=\"TrustPulse Best Social Proof App for WordPress\" width=\"620\" height=\"297\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210785\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/trustpulsebestsocialproofapp.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/trustpulsebestsocialproofapp-300x144.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://trustpulse.com/\" target=\"_blank\">TrustPulse</a> is the most powerful social proof app for business websites. It helps to increase trust, conversions, and sales by displaying attractive social proof notifications on your website. </p>\n<p>It allows you to track purchases, downloads, or registrations on your website, and show them as a recent activity or a count of events. You can choose exactly where and when to display notifications to convert more users into customers. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/trustpulse-social-proof-notification.png\" alt=\"A social proof notification by TrustPulse\" width=\"560\" height=\"222\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-210862\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/trustpulse-social-proof-notification.png 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/trustpulse-social-proof-notification-300x119.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>TrustPulse also works as a FOMO (fear of missing out) plugin as it creates a feeling of urgency with swift notifications. </p>\n<p>This social proof app works well on all <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-website-builders-for-small-business-compared-pros-and-cons/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">popular website platforms</a>, including WordPress, Shopify, Squarespace, Drupal, and more. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://trustpulse.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get started with TrustPulse today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">2. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"WPForms Best WordPress Form Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-158461\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin-300x121.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Customer reviews are among the most powerful social proof elements you can use on your website. </p>\n<p>As user reviews are actual experiences of the real users, consumers find them more trustworthy. According to a study, consumers are 92% more likely to trust their peers over advertising. </p>\n<p>In WordPress, you can easily collect customer reviews and display them on your website using the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> plugin. </p>\n<p>WPForms is the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\">most user-friendly WordPress form plugin</a> which lets you create simple to advanced forms easily and quickly. It comes with tons of pre-designed form templates to allow you to create forms you need in an instant. </p>\n<p>To collect and display user reviews on your website, you can use its blog post submission template with some customization. For more details, see this guide on how to <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-allow-users-to-leave-a-review-on-your-wordpress-site/\" target=\"_blank\">display user reviews on your WordPress site</a>. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get started with WPForms today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">3. OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software.jpg\" alt=\"OptinMonster Best Conversion Optimization Software\" width=\"560\" height=\"260\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155241\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software-300x139.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">OptinMonster</a> is the most powerful lead generation software in the market. It allows you to create stunning popup forms on your website and turn more visitors into subscribers. </p>\n<p>Using OptinMonster, you can create highly customized popups with social proof content. </p>\n<p>For example, you can see the screenshot below. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/socialproofpopupwordpres.png\" alt=\"Social Proof Popup with OptinMonster\" width=\"620\" height=\"408\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210784\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/socialproofpopupwordpres.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/socialproofpopupwordpres-300x197.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>In the image, you can see how our founder <a href=\"https://syedbalkhi.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Syed Balkhi</a>, has added social proof content.</p>\n<p>Also, you can use OptinMonster as a FOMO plugin. It allows you to <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-add-a-countdown-timer-in-wordpress/\">create countdown timer</a> to boost your eCommerce sales. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get started with OptinMonster today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/ovation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Thrive Ovation</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/ovation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/thriveovationtestimonialwpplugin.png\" alt=\"Thrive Ovation WordPress Testimonial Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"242\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210786\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/thriveovationtestimonialwpplugin.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/thriveovationtestimonialwpplugin-300x117.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Similar to the user reviews, testimonials are highly effective social proof content you can use on your website. </p>\n<p>Testimonials are usually words of admiration and recommendation from the happy customers of a business. Adding testimonials to your website helps to increase trust and boost your site conversions. </p>\n<p>Adding testimonials in WordPress is easy with the simple <a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/ovation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Thrive Ovation</a> plugin. It offers you simple ways to gather and display testimonials on your website. </p>\n<p>Thrive Ovation enables you to transform any WordPress comment, social media comment on Facebook and Twitter into a beautiful testimonial with ease. It also lets you create testimonial landing pages to collect testimonials. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/ovation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Thrive Ovation today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/shared-counts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Shared Counts</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/shared-counts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/shared-counts-wordpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"Shared Counts Best WordPress Social Media Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"198\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-162128\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/shared-counts-wordpress-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/shared-counts-wordpress-plugin-300x96.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Displaying social share counts is one of the most popular social proof marketing techniques in use today. </p>\n<p>Most websites display social share buttons and share counts on their blog posts. Doing so helps to prove your credibility, and also urges the new users to share your content.  </p>\n<p>You can easily add share buttons and show the shared counts for your WordPress articles using the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/shared-counts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shared Counts</a> plugin. It is fast and easy to use social media plugin for WordPress. </p>\n<p>Using this plugin, you can insert social share buttons before and/or after post content, and also show the total shares. It includes the popular social platforms Facebook, Pinterest, Yummly, and Twitter, and more. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/shared-counts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Shared Counts today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Constant Contact</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/constantcontact.png\" alt=\"Constant Contact Email Marketing Tool\" width=\"620\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-201594\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/constantcontact.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/constantcontact-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Another simple social proofing technique is to display your email subscribers count. Websites usually add Join XX number of our subscribers message in their email sign-up forms and show that on their sidebars. </p>\n<p>You can see similar email subscription form on our blog, i.e., MonsterInsights Blogs sidebar too.</p>\n<p>You can create similar type of sign-up form on your site by integrating with an <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-email-newsletter-tools-compared-pros-and-cons/\">email marketing service</a>. While therere many options in the market, we recommend you to use <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Constant Contact</a>. </p>\n<p>It is the best email marketing software which lets you create an <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/why-collect-emails-benefits-of-building-an-email-list/\">email list</a> easily and send highly effective emails to your subscribers. </p>\n<p>The best way to create a signup form in WordPress with Constant Contact integration is by using WPForms plugin. </p>\n<p>It lets you connect your sign up form with your Constant Contact account and show the number of subscribers in WordPress. For more details, see this guide on <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/docs/how-to-connect-constant-contact-with-wpforms/\" target=\"_blank\">connecting Constant Contact with WPForms</a>. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Constant Contact today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/beeketing-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Beeketing for WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/beeketing-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/beeketingforwoocommerce.png\" alt=\"Beeketing for WooCommerce Social Proof Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"225\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210787\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/beeketingforwoocommerce.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/beeketingforwoocommerce-300x109.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you have a <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-woocommerce-store/\">WooCommerce store</a>, then you can show many types of social proof statistics to your store visitors. </p>\n<p>For example, you can display how many people viewed and bought products. Similarly, you can show who recently purchased your product. </p>\n<p>If you want these features, then <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/beeketing-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Beeketing for WooCommerce</a> is the perfect plugin for you. It is a free <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-woocommerce-plugins-and-extensions/\">WordPress WooCommerce plugin</a> with plenty of amazing features. </p>\n<p>Not just social proof, it also includes many FOMO plugin features. You can add a sale countdown clock, low-stock indicator, limited time discounts, etc. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/beeketing-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Beeketing for WooCommerce today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to find the best social proof WordPress plugins to boost your sales. You may also want to see our handpicked list of <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers/\">best WordPress plugins</a> to grow your website faster. </p>\n<p>And dont forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more WordPress tips.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-social-proof-wordpress-plugins-to-boost-your-sales/\">7 Best WordPress Plugins &#038; Tools to Add Social Proof and Boost Your Sales [2019]</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-social-proof-wordpress-plugins-to-boost-your-sales/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"Announcing MonsterInsights 7.7  LifterLMS Integration, Expanded Page Insights, and More\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:181:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/announcing-monsterinsights-7-7-lifterlms-integration/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=announcing-monsterinsights-7-7-lifterlms-integration\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/announcing-monsterinsights-7-7-lifterlms-integration/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 20 Jun 2019 14:12:37 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"page insights\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"lifterlms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"LMS plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"site health check\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/?p=210750\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:695:\"<p>For the past few weeks, our developers have been working hard on improving MonsterInsights and adding a new integration. Today were excited to announce the release of MonsterInsights 7.7, which comes with easy LifterLMS tracking and improvements to our admin bar page insights. Plus, it also integrates with the new WordPress Site Health Check feature! [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/announcing-monsterinsights-7-7-lifterlms-integration/\">Announcing MonsterInsights 7.7 &#8211; LifterLMS Integration, Expanded Page Insights, and More</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Keri Engel\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5135:\"<p>For the past few weeks, our developers have been working hard on improving MonsterInsights and adding a new integration.</p>\n<p>Today were excited to announce the release of MonsterInsights 7.7, which comes with easy <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/lifterlms/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">LifterLMS</a> tracking and improvements to our admin bar page insights. Plus, it also integrates with the new WordPress Site Health Check feature!</p>\n<p>Here are all the details&#8230;</p>\n<h3>One-Click LifterLMS eCommerce Analytics</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/lifterlms/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">LifterLMS</a> is a learning management system plugin that lets you easily create and sell courses online. </p>\n<p>Selling courses is a great way to <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/make-money-online/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">make money online</a>. Truly understanding your audience is crucial for the success of your online courses. But keeping track of all the data on your subscriptions and downloads can be a hassle in Google Analytics.</p>\n<p>Thats why weve added one-click setup of LifterLMS tracking to MonsterInsights.</p>\n<p>Now with the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/addon/ecommerce/\">MonsterInsights eCommerce addon</a>, its easier than ever to track all your online course sales and downloads!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/monsterinsights-lifterlms-ecommerce-tracking.png\" alt=\"LifterLMS ecommerce analytics tracking\" width=\"620\" height=\"541\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210753\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/monsterinsights-lifterlms-ecommerce-tracking.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/monsterinsights-lifterlms-ecommerce-tracking-300x262.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<h3>Extended Page Insights &#8211; See Any Page&#8217;s Stats at a Glance</h3>\n<p>With Page Insights addon, you can quickly see stats for your WordPress posts or pages. The Page Insights addon allows you to quickly view important metrics like: new visitors, page views, bounce rate, time on page, page load time, and exits.</p>\n<p>Now, weve extended this feature so that it works for ALL content on your site &#8211; not just single posts and pages.</p>\n<p>Thats right, now you can instantly see the stats of any content, including custom post types, product category pages, and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/form-pages-addon/\" title=\"Form Landing Pages for WPForms\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">form landing pages</a>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/monsterinsights-page-insights-reports.jpg\" alt=\"wordpress page insights analytics\" width=\"620\" height=\"370\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-168228\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/monsterinsights-page-insights-reports.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/monsterinsights-page-insights-reports-300x179.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<h3>WordPress Site Health Checks Integration</h3>\n<p>Did you know that WordPress 5.2 included a new feature called Site Health? It monitors your site automatically and helps you to debug common issues.</p>\n<p>MonsterInsights now integrates with Site Health Check in WordPress, so you can double check your setup at a glance:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/monsterinsights-site-health-check.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights WordPress site health check\" width=\"560\" height=\"495\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210754\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/monsterinsights-site-health-check.png 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/monsterinsights-site-health-check-300x265.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>All these new features are available now, so <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/pricing/\">click here to get started with MonsterInsights Pro today</a>!</p>\n<p>Thats all for this update! The whole team here thanks you for all your support in making MonsterInsights the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" title=\"Best Google Analytics Plugin for WordPress\">best Google analytics WordPress plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>Want to be the first to know about the next release? Be sure to subscribe to our email newsletter and follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>.</p>\n<p><em>Keri and the MonsterInsights Team</em></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/announcing-monsterinsights-7-7-lifterlms-integration/\">Announcing MonsterInsights 7.7 &#8211; LifterLMS Integration, Expanded Page Insights, and More</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/announcing-monsterinsights-7-7-lifterlms-integration/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"How To Find the Most Popular Pages on a WordPress Website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:199:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-find-your-most-popular-blog-posts-with-monsterinsights/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-to-find-your-most-popular-blog-posts-with-monsterinsights\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:102:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-find-your-most-popular-blog-posts-with-monsterinsights/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 17 Jun 2019 12:00:23 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"reports\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"popular posts\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"list building\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"find most popular content on a website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/?p=100858\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:694:\"<p>Are you having difficulty finding the most popular pages on your website? The most reliable tool to find popular posts is through Google Analytics. However, navigating through Google Analytics and understanding its reports can be complicated and time-consuming. In WordPress, MonsterInsights plugin connects your website with Google Analytics and makes it effortless to find popular [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-find-your-most-popular-blog-posts-with-monsterinsights/\">How To Find the Most Popular Pages on a WordPress Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Shahzad Saeed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11075:\"<p>Are you having difficulty finding the most popular pages on your website? The most reliable tool to find popular posts is through Google Analytics. However, navigating through Google Analytics and understanding its reports can be complicated and time-consuming. </p>\n<p>In WordPress, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">MonsterInsights</a> plugin connects your website with Google Analytics and makes it effortless to find popular blogs, landing pages, videos, and other posts.</p>\n<p>In this article, well show you how to find the best pages of a WordPress website using MonsterInsights.</p>\n<h3>Why Use MonsterInsights to Find Popular Posts in WordPress?</h3>\n<p>The conventional way of identifying top performing webpages is through <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/the-complete-beginners-guide-to-google-analytics-for-wordpress/\">Google Analytics</a>. However, thats easier said than done. </p>\n<p>The first step is to set up Google Analytics for your website. And if you plan to do that <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-add-google-analytics-to-wordpress-without-a-plugin/\">without a plugin</a>, then beware of issues such as loss of tracking code, setting up custom event tracking, and download tracking. </p>\n<p>The problems dont just stop there, if you decide to switch to a new theme, you will have to configure Google Analytics tracking code once again. All this is time consuming, complicated, and would require the technical expertise of a developer. </p>\n<p>But luckily, MonsterInsights makes it easy to <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-properly-setup-google-analytics-in-wordpress/\">integrate Google Analytics in WordPress</a> and lets you stay ahead of the game. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/pricing/\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/monsterinsightsbestgapluginforwordpress.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights Best Google Analytics Plugin for WordPress\" width=\"620\" height=\"320\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-186638\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/monsterinsightsbestgapluginforwordpress.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/monsterinsightsbestgapluginforwordpress-300x155.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>MonsterInsights is the best Google Analytics plugin for WordPress. It helps you to easily track your most important website stats, including the most popular content using Google Analytics.</p>\n<h3>How to View Popular Pages in WordPress using MonsterInsights?</h3>\n<p>To get started, you will need to <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-properly-setup-google-analytics-in-wordpress/\">set up Google Analytics on your WordPress website using MonsterInsights</a>. It is an easy process with just a few steps. </p>\n<p>Once the setup is done, you will see changes to your WordPress dashboard as soon as you log in. You will immediately see a <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/introducing-google-analytics-dashboard-widget-for-monsterinsights/\">dashboard widget for MonsterInsights</a> showing your website&#8217;s Overview Report. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsightsdashboardwidget.png\" alt=\"Google Analytics Dashboard Widget for WordPress by MonsterInsights\" width=\"620\" height=\"420\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-154759\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsightsdashboardwidget.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsightsdashboardwidget-300x203.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>The report displays a quick summary of your website audience from the last 30 days. This report is customizable that you can choose the reports you want to see. Select Top Posts / Pages from the options to view popular pages. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/customize-mi-dashboard-widget-stats.jpg\" alt=\"Customize MonsterInsights Dashboard Widget Stats\" width=\"620\" height=\"408\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-162935\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/customize-mi-dashboard-widget-stats.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/customize-mi-dashboard-widget-stats-300x197.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>You can also access the MonsterInsights dashboard report in WordPress by going to <strong>Insights &raquo; Reports</strong> from your dashboard. Then scroll down in the Overview Report and view the &#8216;Top Posts / Pages.&#8217; </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Overview-Report-Top-Posts-and-Pages-MonsterInsights-e1530311718591.jpg\" alt=\"Overview Report - Top Posts and Pages - MonsterInsights\" width=\"1200\" height=\"750\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-148972\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Overview-Report-Top-Posts-and-Pages-MonsterInsights-e1530311718591.jpg 1200w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Overview-Report-Top-Posts-and-Pages-MonsterInsights-e1530311718591-300x188.jpg 300w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Overview-Report-Top-Posts-and-Pages-MonsterInsights-e1530311718591-768x480.jpg 768w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Overview-Report-Top-Posts-and-Pages-MonsterInsights-e1530311718591-1024x640.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></p>\n<p>If you want more details, click on View Full Post/Page Report and evaluate each posts pageviews, average time on page, bounce rate, etc. </p>\n<h3>How to Analyze Reports and Optimize Your Website?</h3>\n<p>MonsterInsights helps to find the most popular pages on your website in just a few clicks. However, thats just the start. </p>\n<p>Once you have a full report on the top pages of a website, you can work on creating killer content that resonates with your audience. </p>\n<h4>1. Create Powerful Data-Driven Content Using MonsterInsights</h4>\n<p>MonsterInsights most popular posts / pages report helps to <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-get-brilliant-blog-post-ideas-from-google-analytics/\">get brilliant blog post ideas</a> for your blog. </p>\n<p>You can evaluate which pages are performing well and which are not. By analyzing the content, you can identify the <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/73-type-of-blog-posts-that-are-proven-to-work/\">type of blog posts</a> that are most popular with your visitors. </p>\n<p>Lets say, among various types of blog posts, list posts bring in the highest traffic and are among the top performing pages on your website. You can use this information to create more listing articles and convert your visitors into potential customers. </p>\n<p>MonsterInsights also helps to <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-see-your-least-performing-wordpress-pages-and-tips-to-improve-them/\">pinpoint pages and posts that are not performing well</a>. For example, you can view your top exit pages by going to <strong>Insights &raquo; Reports &raquo; Publshers</strong> page from your dashboard. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/top-exit-pages-mi-publishers-report.jpg\" alt=\"Top Exit Pages Reports on MonsterInsights \" width=\"560\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-156005\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/top-exit-pages-mi-publishers-report.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/top-exit-pages-mi-publishers-report-300x267.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>You can then optimize these pages to help rank better on the search engines, change their content type, and stop from creating content that doesnt work.  </p>\n<h4>2. Optimize Your Top Pages for More Conversions</h4>\n<p>Your most visited pages have the best potential to convert users into customers. Hence optimizing those pages can help to generate more revenue for your business. </p>\n<p>For example, you can add transactional content, <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-create-the-perfect-call-to-action/\" target=\"_blank\">call to action</a> buttons, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-track-adsense-in-google-analytics-to-optimize-your-revenue/\">ads</a>, and more to these pages. Using such elements at the precise spots on your most popular pages help to increase your website conversions. </p>\n<p>You can use MonsterInsights <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-use-scroll-tracking-in-wordpress-with-google-analytics\">automatic scroll depth tracking</a> to identify the perfect places to add the transactional content. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/scroll-tracking-in-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"Scroll Tracking in WordPress with MonsterInsights Google Analytics Plugin\" width=\"560\" height=\"324\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-199030\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/scroll-tracking-in-wordpress.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/scroll-tracking-in-wordpress-300x174.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>Also, you can optimize your most popular pages for user experience and engagement. Doing so helps to reduce bounce rate, and improves your sales. </p>\n<p>Here are a few things you can do to optimize user experience and engagement:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You can check your page load time, and <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/wordpress-performance-speed/\">optimize page speed</a>.</li>\n<li>Add interactive content like infographics, images, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-survey-in-wordpress/\">surveys</a>, etc.\n</ul>\n<p>When optimized, your most popular pages can bring you more traffic as well as more revenue. </p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to learn how to find the most popular pages on your WordPress website, and create content that never goes flat.</p>\n<p>Using the data on your best posts, you will never have a problem creating a content strategy that falls behind or fails to grow your business. </p>\n<p>You may also want to see our guide on how to <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-check-the-number-of-visitors-for-your-wordpress-site/\">check the number of visitors for your WordPress website</a>. </p>\n<p>And dont forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more helpful Google Analytics tips.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-find-your-most-popular-blog-posts-with-monsterinsights/\">How To Find the Most Popular Pages on a WordPress Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:99:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-find-your-most-popular-blog-posts-with-monsterinsights/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"How to Create an Order Form in WordPress (The Easy Way)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:183:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-an-order-form-in-wordpress-the-easy-way/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-to-create-an-order-form-in-wordpress-the-easy-way\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:94:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-an-order-form-in-wordpress-the-easy-way/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 13 Jun 2019 18:34:03 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"order form\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WordPress order form\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"order form template\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/?p=209477\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:604:\"<p>Do you want to create an order form on your WordPress site? Adding an order form to your website lets you collect orders and payments online, and helps to increase your sales. In this article, well show you how to create a simple order form in WordPress (the easy way). Choosing the Right Plugin for [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-an-order-form-in-wordpress-the-easy-way/\">How to Create an Order Form in WordPress (The Easy Way)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16922:\"<p>Do you want to create an order form on your WordPress site? Adding an order form to your website lets you collect orders and payments online, and helps to increase your sales. </p>\n<p>In this article, well show you how to create a simple order form in WordPress (the easy way). </p>\n<h3>Choosing the Right Plugin for Your WordPress Order Form</h3>\n<p>WordPress comes with many <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\">form builder plugins</a> that allow you to create an order form; however, many of them arent user-friendly. </p>\n<p>But thankfully <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> solves this problem by offering a simple solution for beginners. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"WPForms Best WordPress Form Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-158461\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin-300x121.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> is the most beginner-friendly WordPress form plugin available in the market. </p>\n<p>It comes with a built-in order form template which lets you create a WordPress order form within a few minutes. </p>\n<p>When your forms are ready, it allows you to embed them on your website sidebars, posts, and pages easily with widgets. </p>\n<p>Not only that, you can use WPForms for every type of form youll ever need on your site, including a <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-contact-form-in-wordpress-the-simple-way/\">simple contact form</a>, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-survey-in-wordpress/\">survey form</a>, and more. </p>\n<p>Now lets take a look at how to create a simple order form in WordPress using WPForms (step by step). </p>\n<h3>Step 1: Create a Simple Order Form in WordPress</h3>\n<p>First thing you need to do is install and activate the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms plugin</a> on your WordPress site. For more details, see this guide on <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/step-by-step-guide-to-install-a-wordpress-plugin-for-beginners/\" targe=\"_blank\">how to install a WordPress plugin</a>. </p>\n<p>Once the plugin is activated, go to <strong>WPForms &raquo; Add New</strong> to create a new form. </p>\n<p>After that, itll open the setup page with different form templates. Choose the Billing / Order Form. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/selectbillingorderformtemplateinwpforms.png\" alt=\"Select Billing / Order Form Template in WordPress WPForms\" width=\"620\" height=\"556\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209499\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/selectbillingorderformtemplateinwpforms.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/selectbillingorderformtemplateinwpforms-300x269.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Now WPForms will create a simple order form for you. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/billingorderformsetupscreen.png\" alt=\"WPForms Order Form Setup Screen\" width=\"620\" height=\"427\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209500\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/billingorderformsetupscreen.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/billingorderformsetupscreen-300x207.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>You can customize the form easily by using the simple drag and drop form editor. Herere the main customization options and how to do them. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Customize any field by simply clicking on it, and editing the options</li>\n<li>Rearrange the order of the fields by dragging them up and down</li>\n<li>Add additional fields by dragging them from the left side panel to the right side panel.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You can customize all the available fields, add new fields, and make an order form as you want. </p>\n<p>While you can use most fields as theyre by default, you may want to change the Available Items section. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/editavailableoptionsforwporderform.png\" alt=\"Edit Available Items on WordPress Order Form\" width=\"620\" height=\"402\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209502\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/editavailableoptionsforwporderform.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/editavailableoptionsforwporderform-300x195.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Upon clicking on the Available Items field, the editing options will appear on the left-hand panel. You can rename the items, change the pricing, add more products, or delete the items. </p>\n<p>Check the Use image choices if you want to show the images alongside your items in your order form. </p>\n<p>When youre happy with your order form, click the Save button on the top right corner. </p>\n<h3>Step 2: Configure Your Order Form Settings</h3>\n<p>Now that youve built an order form, the next step is to configure its settings. </p>\n<p>Click on the <strong>Settings</strong> tab and then youll see different settings. At first, the General settings will open where you can customize your form name, description, submit button label, and anti-spam options. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderformgeneralsettings.png\" alt=\"WordPress Order Form General Settings\" width=\"620\" height=\"418\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209507\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderformgeneralsettings.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderformgeneralsettings-300x202.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Second, you can customize Notifications for your order form. At first, you can see a default notification setting. This notification will send notification emails to the admin of your website. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderformdefaultnotification.png\" alt=\"WordPress Order Form Default Notification Settings\" width=\"620\" height=\"372\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209508\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderformdefaultnotification.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderformdefaultnotification-300x180.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>You can also add new notification to send emails to your users who submit your order form. Click on the Add New Notification button, and then name your notification. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/addnewnotificationfororderform.png\" alt=\"Add New Notification for Order Form\" width=\"620\" height=\"233\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209509\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/addnewnotificationfororderform.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/addnewnotificationfororderform-300x113.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>After that, click Show Smart Tags option next to the <strong>Send to Email Address</strong> field. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/showsmarttags-wpforms.png\" alt=\"Show Smart Tags in WPForms Notification Settings\" width=\"620\" height=\"302\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209510\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/showsmarttags-wpforms.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/showsmarttags-wpforms-300x146.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Select the Email option. After that, WPForms will automatically select the field where users enter email address and add that to <strong>Send to Email Address</strong> field. For example, {field_id=&#8221;1&#8243;} in the screenshot below. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/addemailinsendtoemailaddressfield.png\" alt=\"Add Email Option in Send to Email Address Field\" width=\"611\" height=\"447\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209511\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/addemailinsendtoemailaddressfield.png 611w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/addemailinsendtoemailaddressfield-300x219.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 611px) 100vw, 611px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, you can delete the {admin_email} tag from there because its used for sending email to the website admin. </p>\n<p>Next, you can change your notifications email subject, from name, email, reply to, and message. For example, you can compose a message like below in the screenshot. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderconfirmationmessage-wpforms.png\" alt=\"Order Confirmation Notification Email\" width=\"611\" height=\"281\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209512\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderconfirmationmessage-wpforms.png 611w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderconfirmationmessage-wpforms-300x138.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 611px) 100vw, 611px\" /></p>\n<p>Third, you can click on the Confirmation option to configure what to show your users after they submit your order form. </p>\n<p>Therere 3 confirmation types you can use in WPForms: </p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Message</strong>  A simple confirmation message that will appear when users successfully submit your order form.</li>\n<li><strong> Show page</strong>  Redirects the users to a page like Thank You page after they complete your order form.</li>\n<li><strong> Go to URL (Redirect) </strong> &#8211; Redirects the users to any page on your website or another website.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>You can choose any one confirmation type and configure its options.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/confirmationsettingfororderform.png\" alt=\"Confirmation Settings for Order Form in WordPress\" width=\"611\" height=\"358\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209513\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/confirmationsettingfororderform.png 611w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/confirmationsettingfororderform-300x176.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 611px) 100vw, 611px\" /></p>\n<p>Once done, dont forget to click the Save button at the top right corner to save all your form settings. </p>\n<h3>Step 3: Configure Your Payment Settings</h3>\n<p>The next step is to configure payment settings for your order form. Simply click on the <strong>Payments</strong> tab to get started. </p>\n<p>WPForms comes with simple integration for PayPal and Stripe to collect online payments. To use these payments, you need to first install and activate the respective addons by going to <strong>WPForms &raquo; Addons</strong> page from your dashboard. </p>\n<p>After that, you can easily configure payment options for your order form. Once done, dont forget to click the Save button at the top. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderformpayments.png\" alt=\"WordPress Order Form Payment Settings\" width=\"611\" height=\"345\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209514\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderformpayments.png 611w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderformpayments-300x169.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 611px) 100vw, 611px\" /></p>\n<h3>Step 4: Add Your Order Form to Your WordPress Site</h3>\n<p>WPForms allows you to add your order form to many places on your website, like blog posts, pages, and sidebars. </p>\n<p>To add your order form to your WordPress post or page, you can use the WPForms widget in your content edit screen. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/addwpformswidgetinwpblogpost.png\" alt=\"Add WPForms Widget in WordPress Content Edit Screen\" width=\"611\" height=\"345\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209515\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/addwpformswidgetinwpblogpost.png 611w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/addwpformswidgetinwpblogpost-300x169.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 611px) 100vw, 611px\" /></p>\n<p>After the WPForms widget is added to the content area, you need to select the Billing / Order Form that you created earlier. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/selectorderformtoaddinyourpost.png\" alt=\"Select Order Form to Add in Your WordPress Blog Post\" width=\"611\" height=\"405\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209517\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/selectorderformtoaddinyourpost.png 611w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/selectorderformtoaddinyourpost-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 611px) 100vw, 611px\" /></p>\n<p>Similarly, you can also add your order form to the widget-ready areas on your site like the sidebar. </p>\n<p>Go to <strong>Appearance &raquo; Widgets</strong> and drag the WPForms widget to your sidebar. Next, you need to select the Billing / Order form from the drop-down menu and save the widget. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/addorderformtowordpresssidebar.png\" alt=\"Add Order Form to Your WordPress Sidebar\" width=\"611\" height=\"326\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209520\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/addorderformtowordpresssidebar.png 611w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/addorderformtowordpresssidebar-300x160.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 611px) 100vw, 611px\" /></p>\n<p>Once done, you can preview your order form live on your site. Heres how the order form looked on your demo website. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderformlivepreviewinwp.png\" alt=\"WordPress Order Form in a Demo Website\" width=\"620\" height=\"537\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209521\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderformlivepreviewinwp.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/orderformlivepreviewinwp-300x260.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<h3>Track Your WordPress Form Conversions</h3>\n<p>Once you publish your order form, you may get curious about its performance. You want to know how many users are viewing, and actually submitting it. </p>\n<p>If you want to see how your order forms are actually performing, then <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">MonsterInsights</a> plugin is the best solution. It&#8217;s the most user-friendly Google Analytics plugin for WordPress. </p>\n<p>It comes with a simple <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/addon/forms/\">Forms Tracking Addon</a> to let you track your WordPress forms easily. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/forms-report-monsterinsights.jpg\" alt=\"Forms Tracking Report in MonsterInsights\" width=\"620\" height=\"630\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-157484\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/forms-report-monsterinsights.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/forms-report-monsterinsights-295x300.jpg 295w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>For more details, see our guide on <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-track-wpforms-conversions-with-google-analytics/\">how to track WPForms conversions with Google Analytics</a>. </p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to learn how to create an order form in WordPress easily. You may also want to see our guide on <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-survey-in-wordpress/\">how to create a survey in WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>And dont forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more helpful WordPress tutorials.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-an-order-form-in-wordpress-the-easy-way/\">How to Create an Order Form in WordPress (The Easy Way)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:91:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-an-order-form-in-wordpress-the-easy-way/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:37:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:10:{s:6:\"server\";s:13:\"nginx/1.15.10\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Sun, 14 Jul 2019 05:03:30 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:10:\"set-cookie\";s:98:\"srv_id=9c4564d9ab24308e506a24325193b11c; expires=Sun, 14-Jul-19 06:03:30 GMT; max-age=3600; path=/\";s:13:\"last-modified\";s:29:\"Fri, 12 Jul 2019 17:54:12 GMT\";s:4:\"etag\";s:34:\"\"363f9ab155858cabf94d6a9e25a5158d\"\";s:12:\"x-robots-tag\";s:15:\"noindex, follow\";s:4:\"link\";s:68:\"<https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-json/>; rel=\"https://api.w.org/\"\";s:9:\"x-backend\";s:22:\"awesomemotive-web3.com\";s:25:\"strict-transport-security\";s:13:\"max-age=86400\";}}s:5:\"build\";s:14:\"20190712144711\";}'