:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://wpforms.com/?p=496348\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:576:\"<p>Want to get WPForms completely for free? You can use WPForms Lite without spending a penny. In this post, we&#8217;ll show you how to get an unlimited free WPForms trial by using WPForms Lite. What Is WPForms Lite? WPForms Lite is the free version of WPForms, the world&#8217;s most popular WordPress form plugin. It lets [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/unlimited-free-trial-wpforms/\">How to Get an Unlimited Free Trial of WPForms (100% Free Forever)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Lisa Gennaro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9801:\"<p>Want to get WPForms completely for free? You can use WPForms Lite without spending a penny. In this post, we&#8217;ll show you how to get an unlimited free WPForms trial by using WPForms Lite.</p>\n<h3>What Is WPForms Lite?</h3>\n<p>WPForms Lite is the free version of WPForms, the world&#8217;s most popular WordPress form plugin. It lets you easily create, save, and publish forms on your WordPress websitewithout writing a single line of code.</p>\n<p>So how much is WPForms? You&#8217;ll be happy to learn that the WPForms Lite plugin is free, forever.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpforms-lite/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-492292\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wpforms-most-user-friendly-wordpress-contact-form-plugin-in-the-market.jpg\" alt=\"wpforms most user friendly wordpress contact form plugin in the market\" width=\"558\" height=\"336\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wpforms-most-user-friendly-wordpress-contact-form-plugin-in-the-market.jpg 558w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wpforms-most-user-friendly-wordpress-contact-form-plugin-in-the-market-300x181.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px\" /></a></p>\n<p>And with this free trial of WPForms Lite (that never expires), you&#8217;ll get access to features that let you do things like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Create online forms for your site without writing any code</li>\n<li>Add and remove form fields easily with a drag and drop builder</li>\n<li>Collect leads with email subscription forms for your<a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/beginners-guide-to-email-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">email marketing</a></li>\n<li>Display beautiful <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/features/responsive-mobile-friendly/\">mobile-responsive</a> forms on your site</li>\n<li>Prevent spam submissions with <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/features/spam-protection/\">reCAPTCHA and Honeypot</a></li>\n<li>Get access to WPForms support</li>\n</ul>\n<p>On top of that, if you ever decide to <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/docs/upgrade-wpforms-lite-paid-license/\">upgrade your WPForms account from Lite to Pro</a> (which is incredibly easy), you&#8217;ll instantly get access to additional WPForms addons and premium features that let you do things like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Accept payments online via PayPal and Stripe through web order forms</li>\n<li>Make beautiful <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/conversational-forms-addon/\">Conversational Forms</a></li>\n<li>Gather visitor insights with<a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/surveys-and-polls-addon/\">surveys and polls</a></li>\n<li>Use smart conditional logic to show or hide fields:</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/features/conditional-logic/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-462788 size-full\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/nps-survey-enhanced-form-wpforms.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"562\" height=\"628\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Collect user locations with the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/geolocation-addon/\">Geolocation addon</a></li>\n<li>Capture partial form entries with the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/form-abandonment-addon/\">Form Abandonment addon</a></li>\n<li>Get priority customer support</li>\n<li>And <a href=\"http://wpforms.com/pricing\">a ton more</a>&#8230;</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How Do I Get a WPForms Trial for Free?</h3>\n<p>It&#8217;s easy to get WPForms free. To activate your unlimited free WPForms trial, all you need to do is download and install WPForms Lite.</p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\"><p>Make sure you learn why you must avoid any <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/wpforms-pro-nulled/\">WPForms Pro free downloads, WPForms nulled, or a WPForms Pro crack</a>you see floating around the web.</p>\n</div>\n<p>Next, we&#8217;ll walk you throughhow to install WPForms Lite on your WordPress site.</p>\n<h3>How Do I Install WPForms Free Version?</h3>\n<p>So if you&#8217;re ready to get your WPForms trial and download WPForms Lite (it&#8217;s free forever and ever!), make sure you&#8217;re using WordPress.org, not WordPress.com. For more details, check out our post on <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/wordpress-com-vs-wordpress-org-pros-and-cons-compared/\">WordPress.org vs WordPress.com</a>.</p>\n<h3>Step 1:Install the Plugin</h3>\n<p>From your WordPress dashboard, head over to the panel on the left and hover over <strong>Plugins</strong> then select<strong>Add New</strong>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-496429\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/create-smart-wordpress-sites.jpg\" alt=\"create smart wordpress sites\" width=\"1116\" height=\"679\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/create-smart-wordpress-sites.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/create-smart-wordpress-sites-300x183.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/create-smart-wordpress-sites-768x467.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/create-smart-wordpress-sites-1024x623.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, type the keyword &#8220;WPForms&#8221; into the search box on the top right corner.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-496449\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/create-contact-forms-find-wpforms-in-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"create contact forms find wpforms in wordpress\" width=\"1116\" height=\"619\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/create-contact-forms-find-wpforms-in-wordpress.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/create-contact-forms-find-wpforms-in-wordpress-300x166.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/create-contact-forms-find-wpforms-in-wordpress-768x426.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/create-contact-forms-find-wpforms-in-wordpress-1024x568.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, click on the grey<strong> Install Now</strong> button next to the plugin called Contact From by WPForms.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-496451\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/install-wpforms-lite-wordpress-forms-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"install wpforms lite wordpress forms plugin\" width=\"1116\" height=\"619\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/install-wpforms-lite-wordpress-forms-plugin.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/install-wpforms-lite-wordpress-forms-plugin-300x166.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/install-wpforms-lite-wordpress-forms-plugin-768x426.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/install-wpforms-lite-wordpress-forms-plugin-1024x568.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<h3>Step 2:Activate the Plugin</h3>\n<p>Next, click on the blue<strong>Activate</strong>button.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-496613\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/plugin-for-form-entries-with-file-uploads.jpg\" alt=\"plugin for form entries with file uploads\" width=\"1116\" height=\"618\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/plugin-for-form-entries-with-file-uploads.jpg 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/plugin-for-form-entries-with-file-uploads-300x166.jpg 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/plugin-for-form-entries-with-file-uploads-768x425.jpg 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/plugin-for-form-entries-with-file-uploads-1024x567.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>And that&#8217;s it!</p>\n<p>Your WPForms free version is now ready to go and you can start making your first form right away. Next, click the video below to watch a walk-through or read our guide on <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/docs/creating-first-form/\">how to create your first form</a>.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/yDyvSGV7tP4?rel=0\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Brand new to WPForms and looking to get started with the<a href=\"http://wpforms.com/pricing\">WPForms Pro</a>version right away? Check out this post on <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/docs/install-wpforms-plugin/\">how to install and activate the WPForms plugin</a>for help setting up WPForms Pro.</p>\n<p>Wondering what else you can do with WPForms? Check out these articles:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-export-wordpress-form-entries-to-csv/\">How to Export WordPress Form Entries to CSV</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-build-spam-free-wordpress-contact-forms-the-ultimate-guide/\">How to Build Spam-Free WordPress Contact Forms</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/wpforms-power-hacks-to-grow-your-business-online/\">WPForms Power Hacks To Grow Your Business Online</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>In Conclusion</h3>\n<p>So now that you know exactly how to get an WPForms trial and use WPForms for free, tell your friends! And for more free things to use on your website, check out our handy guide of the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-free-wordpress-plugins-for-your-website/\">best free WordPress plugins.</a></p>\n<p>So what are you waiting for? Get started with the <a href=\"http://wpforms.com\">most powerful WordPress forms plugin</a> today.</p>\n<p>And if you like this article, then please follow us on <a href=\"https://facebook.com/wpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> and <a href=\"http://twitter.com/easywpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Twitter</a> for more from the blog.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/unlimited-free-trial-wpforms/\">How to Get an Unlimited Free Trial of WPForms (100% Free Forever)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://wpforms.com/unlimited-free-trial-wpforms/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:25:\"https://wpforms.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:9:{s:6:\"server\";s:13:\"nginx/1.15.10\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Sun, 14 Jul 2019 05:03:31 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:10:\"set-cookie\";s:98:\"srv_id=642bb54d8df0b663ead3557fbe5bd9fa; expires=Sun, 14-Jul-19 06:03:31 GMT; max-age=3600; path=/\";s:13:\"last-modified\";s:29:\"Fri, 12 Jul 2019 21:57:15 GMT\";s:4:\"etag\";s:34:\"\"8832cf12885f1939be14acd25d9ac6ef\"\";s:12:\"x-robots-tag\";s:15:\"noindex, follow\";s:9:\"x-backend\";s:22:\"awesomemotive-web6.com\";s:25:\"strict-transport-security\";s:13:\"max-age=86400\";}}s:5:\"build\";s:14:\"20190712144711\";}', 'no');
