(1236, '_transient_feed_c4b53a17758fd620e8d030cb2580d111', 'a:4:{s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:3:\"rss\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"\n\n\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:7:\"version\";s:3:\"2.0\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:7:\"channel\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"OptinMonster\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"https://optinmonster.com\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:13:\"lastBuildDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sat, 13 Jul 2019 12:14:22 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"language\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"en-US\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"generator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"https://wordpress.org/?v=4.8.3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"item\";a:10:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"10 Best Online Survey Software For Small Businesses (Compared)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://optinmonster.com/best-online-survey-software-for-small-businesses/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://optinmonster.com/best-online-survey-software-for-small-businesses/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 12 Jul 2019 16:53:38 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:7:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"eCommerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"formidable forms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"online survey\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"online survey software\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"survey software\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"wpforms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"https://optinmonster.com/?p=133664\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:626:\"<p>In this article, we&#8217;re going to compare the 10 best online survey software for small businesses. Online surveys are a fast, cheap, and accurate way to reach out and connect with your target audience. They&#8217;re also ridiculously scalable, which means you can easily reach thousands of visitors just as easily as you can reach one. [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-online-survey-software-for-small-businesses/\">10 Best Online Survey Software For Small Businesses (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Jacinda Santora\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20584:\"<p>In this article, we&#8217;re going to compare the 10 best online survey software for small businesses.</p>\n<p>Online surveys are a fast, cheap, and accurate way to reach out and connect with your target audience. They&#8217;re also ridiculously scalable, which means you can easily reach thousands of visitors just as easily as you can reach one.</p>\n<p>When you go about them the right way, by using the best online survey tool, you get access to valuable feedback from the people willing to part with their valuable and hard-earned dollars or time in exchange for what you&#8217;re offering on your site.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s powerful stuff.</p>\n<p>Choosing the best online survey tool can do amazing things for your business. You don&#8217;t have to be a mind reader to know what your customers and potential customers want from youjust ask them.</p>\n<p>To make asking them easier than ever, we&#8217;ve put together this list of the best online survey software for small businesses. Let&#8217;s dive in!</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">1. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-96930 size-full\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/wpforms-e1562928600250.png\" alt=\"wpforms\" width=\"620\" height=\"260\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/wpforms-e1562928600250.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/wpforms-e1562928600250-300x126.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WPForms</a> is hands down the <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-wordpress-form-builder-plugins/\">best WordPress contact form plugin</a> available. The fact that it comes with a powerful and easy-to-use <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/surveys-and-polls-addon/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Survey and Polls addon</a> is what lands it on this list of best online survey software for small businesses.</p>\n<p>You can use the Survey and Polls addon with existing WPForms features like multi-page forms, email integration, and conditional logic to create highly engaging WordPress surveys in the drag and drop form builder with just a few clicks of the mouse.</p>\n<p>The plugin has smart survey fields like the usual text, dropdown, radio button, and checkboxes, but you can also use ratings like stars, hearts, and thumbs up, a Likert scale, and even more!</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133667\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforms-rating-icons.png\" alt=\"wpforms rating icons\" width=\"620\" height=\"455\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforms-rating-icons.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpforms-rating-icons-300x220.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>One of the things we love most about WPForms is its robust survey reporting. Many online survey plugins and tools come with lackluster analysis and reporting tools, but not WPForms.</p>\n<p>With WPForms you get beautiful, real-time reports and graphs based on survey responses. You can use a shortcode to show off the survey results on any page of your site, export the reports to share them on social media and in presentations, or even print them to use in your printed marketing materials.</p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\">Want to give &#8217;em the old razzle dazzle? What about a <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-create-a-wordpress-survey-popup/\">WordPress survey popup</a> that asks for feedback before a customer exits your site? You can do it with WPForms and <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/pricing\">OptinMonster</a>!</div>\n<h3><a title=\"Formidable Forms\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/formidable-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">2. Formidable Forms</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Formidable Forms\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/formidable-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-129839\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/formidable-forms.png\" alt=\"formidable forms advanced wordpress form builder\" width=\"620\" height=\"302\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/formidable-forms.png 1201w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/formidable-forms-300x146.png 300w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/formidable-forms-768x374.png 768w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/formidable-forms-1024x499.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for an online survey tool that can go from simple-to-advanced easily, <a title=\"Formidable Forms\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/formidable-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Formidable Forms</a> fills the bill.</p>\n<p>This plugin comes with ready-to-use form fields like checkboxes, dropdowns, and Likert scales and has a simple drag and drop builder that you can use to design the complex surveys of your dreams.</p>\n<p>Formidable Forms also gives you excellent options to show your survey results in eye-catching charts, graphs, tables, histograms, and more, and lets you embed them on your posts and pages.</p>\n<p>Want to share your creations with your email list? Formidable Forms has marketing addons that make it easy to integrate with your email marketing service.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://crowdsignal.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">3. Crowdsignal</a> (formerly Polldaddy)</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://crowdsignal.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133670\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/crowdsignal-best-online-survey-software.png\" alt=\"crowdsignal by automattic\" width=\"620\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/crowdsignal-best-online-survey-software.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/crowdsignal-best-online-survey-software-300x167.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://crowdsignal.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Crowdsignal</a> (formerly Polldaddy) is a <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-wordpress-plugins-to-grow-your-business/\">popular WordPress plugin</a> for surveys and polls. It&#8217;s a WordPress.com product, so you&#8217;ll need a WordPress.com account to get the plugin API.</p>\n<p>This plugin, unlike the others on our list of the best online survey software for small businesses, is solely a surveys and polls plugin; you can&#8217;t use it to create another type of form.</p>\n<p>Like the other online survey tools on our list, Crowdsignal has a simple drag and drop interface for creating WordPress surveys. You can also use different types of questions, like multiple choice, Likert scales, and free text.</p>\n<p>Once you create a survey form, you can share it all over your website, via email, or on your social media accounts to collect responses.</p>\n<p>And, of course, Crowdsignal lets you create and share easy-to-read reports (paid plans only).</p>\n<h3><a title=\"Ninja Forms\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/ninja-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">4. Ninja Forms</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Ninja Forms\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/ninja-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133671\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ninja-forms-best-online-survey-tools.png\" alt=\"ninja forms\" width=\"620\" height=\"287\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ninja-forms-best-online-survey-tools.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ninja-forms-best-online-survey-tools-300x139.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Ninja Forms\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/ninja-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Ninja Forms</a>is a<a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-wordpress-form-builder-plugins/\">popular contact form plugin</a>that offers a ton of extensions that you can use to create any type of WordPress form, including a survey form.</p>\n<p>The core plugin is free to download, and you can directly download it from WordPress.org. <strong>However</strong>, youll need to buy at least two extensions to create a survey form:<strong>Conditional Logic</strong>and<strong>Multi-Part Forms</strong>. You can buy these extensions individually or with a Ninja forms paid plan.</p>\n<p>Using the multi-page forms extension, you can introduce users to the survey on the first page and then show questions on page two. It makes the survey more interactive and eases users into the idea of participating.</p>\n<p>The biggest drawback to Ninja Forms and its extensions is a lack of reporting and data presentation features.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quiz-master-next/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">5. Quiz and Survey Master</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quiz-master-next/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133672\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/quiz-and-survey-master-best-online-survey-software.png\" alt=\"quiz and survey master\" width=\"620\" height=\"242\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/quiz-and-survey-master-best-online-survey-software.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/quiz-and-survey-master-best-online-survey-software-300x117.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quiz-master-next/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Quiz and Survey Master</a> is a plugin thatwas specifically developed for building surveys. It doesn&#8217;t have the greatest user interface, but it makes up for it with a number of useful features geared specifically towards quizzes and surveys. You can download the core plugin for free from the official WordPress plugin repository.</p>\n<p>The core plugin lets you create surveys with all the typical survey and form fields, but you can also use it to create multi-page online surveys and add them on your WordPress site. It&#8217;ll even let you add quizzes with interactive answers, leaderboards, and scoring, as well as sending confirmation and thank you emails.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s where the free fun stops, though. For reporting and analysis, you&#8217;ll need to purchase a premium addon.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-polls/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">6. WP-Polls</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-polls/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133674\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wp-polls-wordpress-plugin.png\" alt=\"wp-polls online survey tools\" width=\"620\" height=\"293\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wp-polls-wordpress-plugin.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wp-polls-wordpress-plugin-300x142.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-polls/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WP-Polls</a> is an easy free option for a simple poll solution. This online survey tool lets you collect basic user responses using checkboxes and radio buttons and show the results right away.</p>\n<p>This is a very simple tool and is a great &#8220;straw poll&#8221; option when you need to make a poll in seconds. You just go to the<strong>Polls</strong>menu from the WordPress dashboard, create a question and add answer choices. Then, add the poll to your site using code or a widget.</p>\n<p>As mentioned earlier, the results are shown right away, but they&#8217;re also saved in a log so you can see how your registered users voted. IP addresses are also included (<a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/the-ultimate-guide-to-wordpress-and-gdpr-compliance-everything-you-need-to-know/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">a potential problem for those of you in the EU</a>) so you can filter out duplicate votes.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/form-maker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">7. Form Maker by 10Web</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/form-maker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133675\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/form-maker-by-10web.png\" alt=\"form maker by 10web\" width=\"620\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/form-maker-by-10web.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/form-maker-by-10web-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/form-maker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Form Maker by 10Web</a> is another WordPress form builder plugin that you can use for creating online surveys. The plugin comes with a survey tool that lets you create multi-page survey forms using conditional logic, as well as a set of the usual form fields like ratings, stars, multiple choice, and the like that you can use for building surveys.</p>\n<p>Like most of the others that made it onto our roundup of the best online survey software for small businesses, Form Maker by 10Web comes with a drag and drop interface that makes creating your online survey or poll really quick and easy.</p>\n<p>Form Maker also comes with several pre-built templates to take the hassle out of designing online surveys while still making sure they come out nice. Or, you can use its custom CSS editor if you want to put your own signature styling to your forms.</p>\n<p>The plugin is extendable with premium addons but misses the mark entirely with no reporting option.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/captainform/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">8. Forms by CaptainForm</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/captainform/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133676\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/forms-by-captainform.png\" alt=\"forms by captainform\" width=\"620\" height=\"293\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/forms-by-captainform.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/forms-by-captainform-300x142.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a simple and user-friendly interface with a wide array of features and flexibility, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/captainform/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Forms by CaptainForm</a> is a great place to start.</p>\n<p>With this plugin, you can create any type of form, from simple contact forms to payment forms toyou guessed itonline survey forms. It has plenty of form and survey fields to choose from and includes conditional logic to filter questions.</p>\n<p>As a site owner, you can post surveys on your popups, sidebars, blog posts, or pages, and choose to receive email and SMS notifications after each form entry.</p>\n<p>And, you can view real-time reports for your surveys.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yop-poll/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">9. YOP Poll</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yop-poll/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133677\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yop-poll-best-online-survey-tool.png\" alt=\"yop poll\" width=\"620\" height=\"293\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yop-poll-best-online-survey-tool.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/yop-poll-best-online-survey-tool-300x142.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yop-poll/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YOP Poll</a> helps you create simple WordPress polls and surveys to collect feedback. Once it&#8217;s created, you can add the poll on your site using widgets or shortcodes, and even run multiple polls on your site at the same time.</p>\n<p>Polls can be duplicated or edited easily, saving you time for other things. And, there&#8217;s a poll scheduling option that lets you get your polls scheduled out so you&#8217;re not stuck watching a clock and timing things juuuuuust right.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/social-polls-by-opinionstage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">10. Opinion Polls</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/social-polls-by-opinionstage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133678\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/opinion-polls-best-online-survey-tool.png\" alt=\"opinion polls by opinionstage\" width=\"620\" height=\"277\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/opinion-polls-best-online-survey-tool.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/opinion-polls-best-online-survey-tool-300x134.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/social-polls-by-opinionstage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Opinion Polls</a> is a good choice for adding different types of interactive content including polls, surveys, quizzes, and slideshows on your WordPress site.</p>\n<p>The plugin includes support for different types of questions like multiple choice, single or multiple selection, open-ended questions, and you can add a <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-create-the-perfect-call-to-action/\">call to action</a> at the end of your survey to collect leads!</p>\n<p>In addition to all the different question types, you can also add images and videos to your surveys to make them more enticing (think BuzzFeed).</p>\n<p>Opinion Polls is easy to use, even when adding interactive content, and you can post completed surveys in different places on your site: blog posts, pages, sidebars, etc.</p>\n<h3>What Is the Best Online Survey Software for Small Businesses?</h3>\n<p>Being the best online survey software for small businesses requires 3 things:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Be easy to use.</li>\n<li>Have great reporting.</li>\n<li>Have all of the features small businesses needand some they can grow into (because they might not be small forever).</li>\n</ol>\n<p>So, what&#8217;s the best online survey tool around? Well, for us it&#8217;s gotta be <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n<p>WPForms is flexible, easy to use, easy to design, and it has <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/features/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">so many features</a> and integrations that it&#8217;d be absurd if it weren&#8217;t so useful. And it still manages to be beginner friendly! Plus, the team behind the product is world-class.<img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.3/72x72/1f60d.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p>For a very strong second place, we&#8217;d go with <a title=\"Formidable Forms\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/formidable-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Formidable Forms</a>.</p>\n<p>We hope you enjoyed learning more about our picks for the best online survey software for small businesses. Collecting feedback from site visitors and customers is vital to keeping your business healthy and growing and choosing the best online survey tool for your company will make all of that a lot easier.</p>\n<p>Let us know in the comments which of the tools strike your fancy. Have you already tried one? Currently using one? Let us know!</p>\n<p>And don&#8217;t forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Optinmonster?sub_confirmation=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YouTube</a>, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/optinmonster\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a>, and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/optinmonster\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> for more useful marketing tips, tools, and advice.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-online-survey-software-for-small-businesses/\">10 Best Online Survey Software For Small Businesses (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://optinmonster.com/best-online-survey-software-for-small-businesses/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"36 Best Lead Generation Tools to Get More Targeted Leads\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://optinmonster.com/best-lead-generation-tools/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://optinmonster.com/best-lead-generation-tools/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 11 Jul 2019 20:50:31 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Lead Generation\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"generate leads\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"lead gen\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"lead generation\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"lead generation tools\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"https://optinmonster.com/?p=129272\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:596:\"<p>Lead generation isn&#8217;t just about getting people to visit your site in the first place. It&#8217;s also about collecting their info so you can contact those visitors, and nurture them into becoming loyal customers and raving fans. To guide them through that journey, you need to use the right lead generation tools. This section has [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-lead-generation-tools/\">36 Best Lead Generation Tools to Get More Targeted Leads</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Jacinda Santora\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43380:\"<p>Lead generation isn&#8217;t just about getting people to visit your site in the first place. It&#8217;s also about collecting their info so you can contact those visitors, and nurture them into becoming loyal customers and raving fans. To guide them through that journey, you need to use the right lead generation tools.</p>\n<p>This section has our picks for tools that&#8217;ll help you <strong>nail every aspect of web-based lead generation</strong>. Choose your favorites, and you&#8217;ll soon be generating more leads and making more sales.</p>\n<p>Here&#8217;s a table of contents to help you explore the list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#lg1\">Our Top Pick For Lead Generation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#lg2\">Email Marketing Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#lg3\">Email Address Finders</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#lg4\">Prospecting and Outreach Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#lg5\">CRM Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#lg6\">Sales Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#lg7\">Communication Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#lg8\">Advertising Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#lg9\">Other Lead Generation Tools</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"lg1\"><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/pricing\">1. OptinMonster</a>: Our Top Pick For Lead Generation</h3>\n<p>Let&#8217;s start with OptinMonster&#8217;s online lead generation software. <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/integrations/\">OptinMonster integrates</a> with all major email marketing and CRM platforms, making it easy to capture, share, and manage leads.</p>\n<p>In fact, our customers have had amazing success using OptinMonster as a lead capture tool.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-100957\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/snacknation.png\" alt=\"snacknation\" width=\"620\" height=\"299\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/snacknation.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/snacknation-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>For example:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Snack Nation earns <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/case-study-snack-nation-adds-1200-segmented-leads/\">1200 new leads each week</a> by using OptinMonster to deliver <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/10-tools-to-help-you-create-quality-content-upgrades/\">content upgrades</a></li>\n<li>Guido&#8217;s, a St. Louis restaurant, used <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/monsterlinks/\">MonsterLinks</a> to trigger an offer for a free appetizer, getting <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/restaurant-marketing-strategies-case-study/\">1000 new leads</a> in less than 4 months</li>\n<li>Wholesale Suite gets <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-wholesale-suite-gains-6500-leads-a-year-using-two-step-optins/\">6500 qualified leads a year</a> by combining 2 step optins with continuous <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/easy-ab-split-testing/\">split testing</a>, which is built into OptinMonster</li>\n<li>Woodside Communities was able to <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/case-study-woodside-increased-revenue-294435-two-months/\">increase their leads by 476%</a> and shorten their average lead-to-sale time from 3-6 months to just under two weeks.</li>\n<li>Check out the rest of our <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/category/case-studies/\">case studies</a> for even more examples!</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You can also use OptinMonster to jumpstart lead growth with advanced targeting rules for marketing campaigns. These include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/page-level-targeting/\">Page-level targeting</a>, so you can easily run campaigns on different pages, targeted to the page content</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/exit-intent/\">Exit-Intent technology</a>, a proven trigger that gets visitors&#8217; attention just before they leave your site</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/onsite-retargeting/\">OnSite Retargeting</a> so you can create special offers and promotions for returning visitors.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/lead-sharing/\">Lead Sharing</a> features to easily share leads with joint venture and co-marketing partners.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>There&#8217;s more. You can quickly deliver lead magnets with our range of success actions. Plus you can target campaigns by <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/geo-location-targeting/\">location</a>, <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/inactivity-sensor-exit-intent-for-mobile/\">activity or inactivity</a>, <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/device-based-targeting/\">device</a>, and much more.</p>\n<p class=\"om-callout\"><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/pricing/\">Click here to explode your lead generation with OptinMonster today</a>.</p>\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s look at the rest of our lead generation software.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg2\">Email Marketing Tools</h3>\n<p>When it comes to online lead generation, you can&#8217;t beat email marketing. <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/is-email-marketing-dead-heres-what-the-statistics-show/\">The stats show</a> that most people welcome emails from the companies they want to connect with. That makes email marketing software among the best lead gen tools. Here are some <a href=\"http://www.wpbeginner.com/showcase/best-email-marketing-services/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">email marketing services</a> we recommend.</p>\n<p><a title=\"Constant Contact\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>2. Constant Contact</strong></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Constant Contact\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129209\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/constant-contact-lead-gen.png\" alt=\"constant contact email marketing service\" width=\"620\" height=\"328\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/constant-contact-lead-gen.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/constant-contact-lead-gen-300x159.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you have a bigger list, or simply prefer a MailChimp alternative, try <a class=\"thirstylink\" title=\"Constant Contact\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Constant Contact</a>. You&#8217;ll get lots of support to use this lead generation tool. Constant Contact rates highly for world-class support, extensive online training, and webinars to help you achieve success.</p>\n<p><a title=\"Mailjet\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/mailjet/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>3. Mailjet</strong></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Mailjet\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/mailjet/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-132815\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/mailjet-e1559816573731.png\" alt=\"Mailjet\" width=\"620\" height=\"357\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Mailjet\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/mailjet/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Mailjet</a> is a wonderful email marketing service known for high email deliverability. This platform comes with awesome tools like <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/how-to-create-an-email-newsletter/\">email newsletters</a>, transaction emails, marketing automation, and SMS messages.</p>\n<p>You can even send up to 6000 emails to unlimited contacts each month FOR FREE as long as you dont mind including the Mailjet branding.</p>\n<p><a title=\"AWeber\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/aweber-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>4. AWeber</strong></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"AWeber\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/aweber-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129211\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/aweber.png\" alt=\"aweber email marketing service\" width=\"620\" height=\"293\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/aweber.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/aweber-300x142.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"AWeber\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/aweber-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">AWeber</a> is an excellent email marketing tool for automated lead generation. It lets you easily create and send emails, and import content from your blog and share it with subscribers. It also has great analytics.</p>\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve chosen your email marketing tool, check out our <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/beginners-guide-to-email-marketing/\">email marketing guide</a> to get started with email lead generation.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg3\">Email Address Finders</h3>\n<p>Sometimes you&#8217;re going to need to connect with people who aren&#8217;t on your email list. That means finding their email address and contact details. This next batch of tools will help with that.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://hunter.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>5. Hunter</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://hunter.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129212\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hunter.png\" alt=\"hunter - best growth hacks\" width=\"620\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hunter.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hunter-300x164.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you want to do a quick email search, <a href=\"https://hunter.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Hunter</a> is a useful tool. Just type in the domain, and it&#8217;ll find the email address pattern. Hunter also includes a confidence rating so you know if the email is likely to be right.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://aeroleads.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>6. AeroLeads</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://aeroleads.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133657\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/aeroleads-best-lead-generation-tools.png\" alt=\"find emails and phone numbers with aeroleads\" width=\"620\" height=\"174\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/aeroleads-best-lead-generation-tools.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/aeroleads-best-lead-generation-tools-300x84.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://aeroleads.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">AeroLeads</a> provides a Google Chrome plugin to help you search LinkedIn, AngelList, and other networks for leads. Add those to your AeroLeads account, and this lead generation tool will find their business email addresses and other contact details. Then you&#8217;re ready to start reaching out.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.voilanorbert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>7. Voila Norbert</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.voilanorbert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133658\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/voila-norbert-best-lead-generation-tools.png\" alt=\"find anyone\'s email address with voila norbert\" width=\"620\" height=\"229\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/voila-norbert-best-lead-generation-tools.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/voila-norbert-best-lead-generation-tools-300x111.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.voilanorbert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Voila Norbert</a> promises to help you find and verify email addresses. You can search in bulk for prospects with a CSV file. The tool also integrates with a wide range of CRM software. That makes it easy to keep track of your lead generation efforts.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg4\">Prospecting and Outreach Tools</h3>\n<p>Want to turn more of those contacts into leads and sales? These (mostly) automated lead generation tools will help with that process.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.outreachplus.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>8. OutreachPlus</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.outreachplus.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133659\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/outreachplus-best-lead-generation-tools.png\" alt=\"create and send personalized emails with outreachplus\" width=\"620\" height=\"240\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/outreachplus-best-lead-generation-tools.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/outreachplus-best-lead-generation-tools-300x116.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.outreachplus.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">OutreachPlus</a> is one of several multi-purpose lead generation tools in this roundup. It lets you create and send personalized emails while still benefiting from automation. And it helps you find your best prospects for future outreach based on responses to your past or current campaigns.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hoovers.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>9. Hoovers</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hoovers.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120215\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/9-hoovers.jpg\" alt=\"hoovers is online lead generation software\" width=\"620\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/9-hoovers.jpg 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/9-hoovers-300x166.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hoovers.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Hoovers</a> says it&#8217;s the world&#8217;s largest commercial database. You can use it to build targeted lists of new prospects. Hoovers includes company information to help you have more relevant conversations with those prospects. That helps you turn more prospects into leads and sales.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.datanyze.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>10. Datanyze</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.datanyze.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120216\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/10-datanyze.png\" alt=\"top lead management software - datanyze\" width=\"620\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/10-datanyze.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/10-datanyze-300x169.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re in the business of technology, you can find leads based on data about the technology your target customers are already using. That&#8217;s what <a href=\"https://www.datanyze.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Datanyze</a> promises. It includes a prospecting tool to help you find contact details fast. Then you can export those to your CRM software for management and follow-up.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.leadforensics.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>11. Lead Forensics</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.leadforensics.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129214\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/leadforensics.png\" alt=\"lead generation marketing tools - lead forensics\" width=\"620\" height=\"297\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/leadforensics.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/leadforensics-300x144.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Sometimes you can miss out on good leads just because you don&#8217;t know everyone who visits your site. <a href=\"https://www.leadforensics.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Lead Forensics</a> aims to solve that problem by getting contact details for anonymous website visitors. You can also score those prospects so you spend your time on those most likely to convert.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.growbots.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>12. Growbots</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.growbots.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129215\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/growbots.png\" alt=\"use growbots for automated lead generation\" width=\"620\" height=\"366\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/growbots.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/growbots-300x177.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Know the market you want to target? <a href=\"https://www.growbots.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Growbots</a> will choose your best prospects from a database of more than 200 million contacts. You can easily get in touch with the right decision makers and follow up automatically. Growbots also includes testing so you can check which approaches are most effective.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://prospect.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>13. Prospect.io</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://prospect.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120219\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/13-prospectio.png\" alt=\"prospectio is a web based lead generation tool\" width=\"620\" height=\"353\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/13-prospectio.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/13-prospectio-300x171.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://prospect.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Prospect.io</a> handles both prospecting and outreach. It helps you find and verify emails for your prospects. Then you can reach out to them via a range of templates. And you can easily track data on all interactions. Best of all, it integrates with a range of services to get contact information automatically.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg5\">CRM Tools</h3>\n<p>You can&#8217;t do a roundup of lead generation tools without including tools for customer relationship management (CRM). These tools help you connect and keep track of prospects and leads throughout the sales pipeline. Here are our picks.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/products/crm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>14. Hubspot</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/products/crm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-120220\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/14-hubspot-crm.png\" alt=\"hubspot crm - lead generation tools\" width=\"552\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/14-hubspot-crm.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/14-hubspot-crm-300x272.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 552px) 100vw, 552px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Hubspot has a suite of free tools, and <a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/products/crm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Hubspot CRM</a> is just one of them. But it&#8217;s a great way to organize, track and nurture leads. It tracks interactions automatically and helps you and your sales team keep on top of what&#8217;s happening.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.pardot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>15. Pardot</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.pardot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129216\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/pardot.png\" alt=\"pardot lead generation software\" width=\"620\" height=\"276\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/pardot.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/pardot-300x134.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.pardot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Pardot</a> is a well-known lead generation tool that helps you manage and qualify leads. That ensures that you&#8217;re always talking to the best leads. Pardot includes fine-grained segmentation and automation for better communication with your future customers.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sharpspring.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>16. SharpSpring</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sharpspring.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129217\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/sharpspring.png\" alt=\"lead capture tools - sharpspring\" width=\"620\" height=\"283\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/sharpspring.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/sharpspring-300x137.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>In addition to its own built-in CRM, <a href=\"https://sharpspring.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">SharpSpring</a> integrates with all the top CRM lead management tools. That allows you to manage lead data across multiple platforms. SharpSpring includes custom deal stages and a useful pipeline overview, as well as other marketing tools.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.contactually.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>17. Contactually</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.contactually.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120223\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/17-contactually.jpg\" alt=\"contactually lead generation software\" width=\"620\" height=\"347\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/17-contactually.jpg 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/17-contactually-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>It only takes a click to start managing your Google or Office365 contacts with <a href=\"https://www.contactually.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Contactually</a>. Once they&#8217;re connected, it&#8217;s easy to organize and segment contacts. You can also optimize workflow and schedule communication with Contactually&#8217;s AI tools.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://keap.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>18. Keap</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://keap.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133660\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/keap-best-lead-generation-tools.png\" alt=\"keap formerly infusionsoft\" width=\"620\" height=\"133\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/keap-best-lead-generation-tools.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/keap-best-lead-generation-tools-300x64.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://keap.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Keap</a>(formerly Infusionsoft) helps you keep customer information in one location. That lets you track interactions and responsiveness to guide future campaigns. It&#8217;s a multi-functional lead generation tool that&#8217;s definitely worth exploring.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.marketo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>19. Marketo</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.marketo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129635\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/marketo-automated-email-marketing.png\" alt=\"marketo automated email marketing\" width=\"620\" height=\"361\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/marketo-automated-email-marketing.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/marketo-automated-email-marketing-300x175.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The lead management solution from <a href=\"https://www.marketo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Marketo</a> helps businesses form relationships with prospective customers before they talk to sales reps. It helps you attract leads via inbound and outbound marketing, and improve the quality of the leads you get.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.nimble.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>20. Nimble</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.nimble.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129220\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/nimble.png\" alt=\"nimble lead gen tool\" width=\"620\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/nimble.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/nimble-300x207.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.nimble.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Nimble</a> pulls in information from a number of online sources, so you always have the latest data on potential leads. It makes it easy to identify and nurture key contacts without having to do any data entry. It&#8217;s available for major browsers, email programs, and mobile platforms.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.onepagecrm.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>21. OnePageCRM</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.onepagecrm.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120231\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/25-onepagecrm.png\" alt=\"onepagecrm lead gen software\" width=\"620\" height=\"255\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/25-onepagecrm.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/25-onepagecrm-300x123.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Looking for another simple piece of lead generation software? <a href=\"https://www.onepagecrm.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">OnePageCRM</a> grabs leads from Gmail, social media sites, and business networking sites to integrate them into your CRM. This software focuses on &#8220;next action sales,&#8221; so making sales is as simple as checking off your to-do list.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg6\">Sales Tools</h3>\n<p>For businesses, the goal of using lead generation tools is turning those leads into sales. And since the <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/ecommerce-optimization-guide/#eco12\">best source of repeat business</a> is existing customers, it makes sense to use tools that both make sales and nurture your customers. Here are some tools to help with that.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.salesforce.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>22. Salesforce</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.salesforce.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120227\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/21-salesforce.png\" alt=\"salesforce lead generation software\" width=\"620\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/21-salesforce.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/21-salesforce-300x170.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.salesforce.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Salesforce</a> is among the world&#8217;s top sales and lead management software. It includes tools to help you manage leads, customers, sales teams and more. It integrates with a wide range of sales and marketing software to help businesses sell more and deliver better customer service.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/products/sales\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>23. Hubspot Sales</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/products/sales\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-120228\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/22-hubspot-sales.png\" alt=\"hubspot lead generation\" width=\"524\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/22-hubspot-sales.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/22-hubspot-sales-300x286.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 524px) 100vw, 524px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/products/sales\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Hubspot Sales</a> is part of Hubspot&#8217;s suite of free tools for small businesses. It helps you save time on generating new leads. Hubspot Sales includes tools and templates for outreach and follow-up, so you can interact more efficiently with prospective customers.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://business.linkedin.com/sales-solutions/sales-navigator\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>24. LinkedIn Sales Navigator</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://business.linkedin.com/sales-solutions/sales-navigator\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120229\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/23-LinkedIn-Sales-Navigator.jpg\" alt=\"23 LinkedIn Sales Navigator\" width=\"620\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/23-LinkedIn-Sales-Navigator.jpg 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/23-LinkedIn-Sales-Navigator-300x170.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Business networking site LinkedIn has huge amounts of company information in its databases. You can access that info via <a href=\"https://business.linkedin.com/sales-solutions/sales-navigator\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">LinkedIn Sales Navigator</a>. This lead generation tool provides advanced lead searches and recommendations. It also includes CRM integrations and sales updates.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.pipedrive.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>25. Pipedrive</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.pipedrive.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120242\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/24-pipedrive-1.png\" alt=\"pipedrive lead generation software\" width=\"620\" height=\"335\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/24-pipedrive-1.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/24-pipedrive-1-300x162.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.pipedrive.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Pipedrive</a> prides itself on simplicity and it really is easy to use. This piece of automatic lead generation software tracks all interactions with leads easily. Then you can see all the data in one unified dashboard whenever you check in. It also makes it easy to know what action to take next.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg7\">Communication Tools</h3>\n<p>As we mentioned in our article on <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/ecommerce-checkout-page-optimization/#check8\">checkout page optimization</a>, talking to people who land on your site can help you win them as customers. That applies to leads, too. This next batch of lead generation tools will help with communication.</p>\n<p>First, let&#8217;s look at a few live chat tools.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.drift.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>26. Drift</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.drift.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129221\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/drift.png\" alt=\"drift lead gen tools\" width=\"620\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/drift.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/drift-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.drift.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Drift</a> helps you deliver helpful and personal service to customers by having a conversation with them. According to Drift, conversation drives half of all online sales, so this is crucial. This lead generation tool can help you wow your customers, and it includes a free level.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.intercom.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>27. Intercom</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.intercom.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133661\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/intercom-best-lead-generation-tools.png\" alt=\"intercom gives you a totally customizable messaging suite\" width=\"620\" height=\"314\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/intercom-best-lead-generation-tools.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/intercom-best-lead-generation-tools-300x152.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Need a modern messaging service to fully engage site visitors? <a href=\"https://www.intercom.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Intercom</a> could be the answer. As well as being one of the best lead capture tools around, Intercom can help with customer support and onboarding.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bontact.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>28. Bontact</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bontact.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120234\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/28-Bontact.jpg\" alt=\"bontact lead gen tools\" width=\"620\" height=\"308\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/28-Bontact.jpg 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/28-Bontact-300x149.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Thinking of using <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/facebook-messenger-marketing/\">Facebook Messenger</a> or WhatsApp Business to contact your leads? What about another platform? When you use <a href=\"https://bontact.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Bontact</a>, you don&#8217;t have to choose. This lead generation app brings all your messaging under one roof to give you and your customers a unified, but cross-platform, experience.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.callpage.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>29. CallPage</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.callpage.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129222\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/callpage.png\" alt=\"lead gen tools - callpage\" width=\"620\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/callpage.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/callpage-300x162.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.callpage.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">CallPage</a> promises a 5-minute setup. After that, you can immediately start talking to visitors. Once they enter their phone number in the onscreen widget, they can be connected to you within seconds, no matter where they&#8217;re located. That lets you answer their question so you can win their business.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg8\">Advertising Tools</h3>\n<p>If you want to get leads by promoting your business you&#8217;ll need some lead generation tools to advertise your products and services. In addition to using social ads on <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/business/products/ads\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a>, <a href=\"https://business.linkedin.com/marketing-solutions/ads\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">LinkedIn</a>, <a href=\"https://ads.twitter.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a>, and others, here are some more lead generation services to try.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ads.google.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>30. Google Ads</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ads.google.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129223\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/google-adwords.png\" alt=\"adwords content marketing\" width=\"620\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/google-adwords.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/google-adwords-300x176.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ads.google.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">GoogleAds</a>service puts ads in front of people when they search for related terms. That makes the ads relevant and increases the chances that searchers will visit your website or call your business. One great feature is that setting up campaigns is free. You only pay for advertising when people click your ad.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.adroll.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>31. AdRoll</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.adroll.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129224\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/adroll.png\" alt=\"adroll lead gen software\" width=\"620\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/adroll.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/adroll-300x155.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.adroll.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">AdRoll</a> helps display ads, social ads, and email work together to promote your business. It includes automation and rich insights so you can tweak campaigns for more growth.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://adespresso.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>32. AdEspresso</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://adespresso.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-129225\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/adespresso.png\" alt=\"adespresso lead gen\" width=\"620\" height=\"301\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/adespresso.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/adespresso-300x146.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Hootsuite&#8217;s <a href=\"https://adespresso.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">AdEspresso</a> is an optimization tool for Facebook, Instagram, and Google ads. It lets you create and test multiple ad variants with only a few clicks. You can run ads with various audiences, too, and measure what&#8217;s most effective with in-depth analytics.</p>\n<h3 id=\"lg9\">Other Lead Generation Tools</h3>\n<p>Finally, let&#8217;s complete our roundup with a few other lead generation tools.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.extole.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>33. Extole</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.extole.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120238\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/33-Extole.jpg\" alt=\"extole lead gen tools\" width=\"620\" height=\"343\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/33-Extole.jpg 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/33-Extole-300x166.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Word of mouth is a powerful lead generation tool. <a href=\"https://www.extole.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Extole</a> harnesses that by being an advocacy marketing platform. It helps you turn customers into advocates, who then help you generate more leads.</p>\n<p><a title=\"Referral Candy\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/referral-candy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>34. ReferralCandy</strong></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Referral Candy\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/referral-candy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120246\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/34-referralcandy-1.png\" alt=\"referral candy lead gen tools\" width=\"620\" height=\"342\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/34-referralcandy-1.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/34-referralcandy-1-300x165.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Referral Candy\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/referral-candy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">ReferralCandy</a> helps eCommerce stores generate leads and sales by offering customers discounts for referring new business. You can easily customize a referral program for your business, and collect data on how the program is working.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>35. WPForms</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-118698\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/9-wpf-surveys.gif\" alt=\"wpforms survey tool\" width=\"620\" height=\"464\" /></a></p>\n<p>One way to get more leads from website visitors is to find out what they want. You can use <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WPForms</a> to create a poll or survey that gets this important information. Or simply <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-freshsales-lead-form-in-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">integrate their simple drag and drop forms</a> with other lead capture tools.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zapier.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>36. Zapier</strong></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zapier.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-120240\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/36-zapier.png\" alt=\"zapier lead generation software\" width=\"620\" height=\"342\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/36-zapier.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/36-zapier-300x165.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re wondering what Zapier&#8217;s doing on a list of lead generation tools, the answer&#8217;s simple. <a href=\"https://zapier.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Zapier</a>&#8216;s here because it allows you to connect multiple business services together, including some of the lead generation software in our roundup. In fact, they have an <a href=\"https://zapier.com/apps/optinmonster/integrations\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">OptinMonster lead trigger</a> that makes it super easy to connect OptinMonster, the #1 conversion software in the world, with the other business services you use.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s it! 36 of the best lead generation tools to get your list popping, conversions increasing, and your sales soaring. And, if you enjoyed this post, you&#8217;ll absolutely love our MONSTER <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/lead-generation/\">lead generation strategy guide</a>, and our <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-wordpress-plugins-to-grow-your-business/\">roundup of the best WordPress plugins</a>. Go check &#8217;em out.</p>\n<p>OptinMonster is ready and able to take you where you want to go. <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/pricing\">Join us today</a> and find out why <strong>we&#8217;re the best lead generation software out there</strong>!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-lead-generation-tools/\">36 Best Lead Generation Tools to Get More Targeted Leads</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://optinmonster.com/best-lead-generation-tools/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"41 Best WordPress Plugins &amp; Tools of 2019 (Tested and Reviewed)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://optinmonster.com/best-wordpress-plugins-to-grow-your-business/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://optinmonster.com/best-wordpress-plugins-to-grow-your-business/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 11 Jul 2019 19:30:14 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"eCommerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"best wordpress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"email list\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"list building\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"https://optinmonster.com/?p=121696\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:639:\"<p>Wondering what are the best WordPress plugins for business websites? If you&#8217;re just getting started or looking for ways to save a little, then you&#8217;re in the right place. We&#8217;re going to share the best free and premium WordPress plugins of 2019. Since there are over 55,000 WordPress plugins available on the internet, it&#8217;s hard [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-wordpress-plugins-to-grow-your-business/\">41 Best WordPress Plugins &#038; Tools of 2019 (Tested and Reviewed)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Jacinda Santora\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:91008:\"<p>Wondering what are the <strong>best WordPress plugins</strong> for business websites? If you&#8217;re just getting started or looking for ways to save a little, then you&#8217;re in the right place. We&#8217;re going to share the <strong>best free and premium WordPress plugins</strong> of 2019.</p>\n<p>Since there are over 55,000 WordPress plugins available on the internet, it&#8217;s hard for business owners to choose the best WordPress plugin for their need.</p>\n<p>We consulted with top WordPress experts to create the ultimate list of the 41 best WordPress plugins of 2019!</p>\n<p>To make it easy for you, we have created a table of content to break down the best WordPress plugins based on your needs:</p>\n<p><strong>Table of Contents</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#lead_gen_plugins\">Lead Generation Plugins to Grow Your Email List</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#analytics_plugins\">WordPress Analytics Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#contact_form_plugins\">Contact Form Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#affiliate_marketing_plugins\">Affiliate Marketing Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#email_marketing_plugins\">Email Marketing Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#ecommerce_plugins\">eCommerce Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#seo_plugins\">Search Engine Optimization (SEO) Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#page_builder_plugins\">Posting &amp; Page Builder Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#gallery_plugins\">Gallery &amp; Image Optimization Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#site_optimization_plugins\">Site Speed &amp; Optimization Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#security_plugins\">Site Security Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#backup_plugins\">Backup Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#membership_sites_plugins\">Membership Sites &amp; Course Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#social_plugins\">Social Marketing and Sharing Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#scheduling_plugins\">Calendar, Events &amp; Scheduling Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#other_plugins\">Other WordPress Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"lead_gen_plugins\">Best Lead Generation Plugins to Grow Your Email List</h3>\n<h3><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/pricing\">1. OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/pricing\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128668\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/charted-campaign-builder-default.png\" alt=\"charted campaign builder default\" width=\"620\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/charted-campaign-builder-default.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/charted-campaign-builder-default-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/pricing\">OptinMonster</a> is the most powerful conversion optimization and lead generation software in the world. We offer awesome tools for publishers, eCommerce, agencies, and B2B. No matter what it is you do, OptinMonster has a solution for you that will help you get more subscribers, increase sales, and convert more of your web traffic into customers.</p>\n<p>Our drag and drop campaign builder makes it super easy to create beautiful, effective, high-converting optins that are mobile friendly.</p>\n<p>With OptinMonster you can create targeted campaigns using out-of-the-box features like referrer detection, onsite retargeting, geolocation targeting, and cookie retargeting. We also offer seamless integrations with things like your email marketing service so you can easily personalize, segment, and target campaigns with great results.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Campaign triggers like exit-intent and timed display</li>\n<li>Targeted campaigns using referrer detection, location, and cookie retargeting</li>\n<li>Actionable insights like A/B testing, automated personalization, and smart success</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why You Need It:</strong></p>\n<p>Businesses live and die by their leads. When you use OptinMonster you can rest assured that you&#8217;re not getting junk leads that are going nowhere.</p>\n<p>Leads generated through OptinMonster have <strong>higher conversion rates</strong> than cold leads. This is because the leads you get through OptinMonster are highly targeted and <strong>on purpose</strong>. An actual person has indicated that they WANT whatever it is you&#8217;re selling. You don&#8217;t get that with purchased leads.</p>\n<p>With OptinMonster you can <strong>create killer campaigns</strong> in minutes to <strong>keep your leads list growing and converting</strong>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">2. SeedProd</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-130460\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/seedprod-coming-soon-page-builder.png\" alt=\"Seedprod coming soon page builder - best WordPress plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"342\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/seedprod-coming-soon-page-builder.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/seedprod-coming-soon-page-builder-300x165.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SeedProd</a> is the ultimate coming soon page, launch page, under construction page, and maintenance mode plugin for WordPress. So, why is it listed under our lead generation plugins, you ask.</p>\n<p>The answer is simple: SeedProd is a powerful tool for capturing leads <strong>before your WordPress site even goes live</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Built-in email autoresponder</li>\n<li>Search engine optimized</li>\n<li>Social follow and share</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why You Need It:</strong></p>\n<p>Creating a pre-launch coming soon page helps you build your email list and generate buzz about your brand before you&#8217;re even open for business. And, it helps to keep potential customers engaged.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re not new to the game, SeedProd is still for you! You can use SeedProd to create custom maintenance mode and 404 pages that will delight your visitors &#8211; and get you leads!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click here to get started with a risk-free, 14-day trial of SeedProd.</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"analytics_plugins\">Best WordPress Analytics Plugins</h3>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">3. MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-121861\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/monsterinsights-1.png\" alt=\"monsterinsights analytics - best wordpress plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"381\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/monsterinsights-1.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/monsterinsights-1-300x184.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>With the MonsterInsights plugin for WordPress, you can setup analytics in just a few clicks and see at a glance how your website is performing.</p>\n<p>This plugin allows you to understand complicated analytics like traffic sources and audience behavior easily, so you know what&#8217;s working and where you&#8217;re wasting your time. With that information readily available, you can create a data-driven strategy to grow your business.</p>\n<p>MonsterInsights also offers eCommerce tracking to get the data you need on your WooCommerce or Easy Digital Download store.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Quick and easy setup</li>\n<li>eCommerce tracking to keep tabs on your company&#8217;s health</li>\n<li>Real-time stats</li>\n<li>Google Analytics dashboard</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why You Need It:</strong></p>\n<p>Website analytics are vital to the growth of your business and with MonsterInsights you have <strong>real-time access to the data you need</strong>.</p>\n<p>No matter what you sell, MonsterInsights shows you the <strong>most important eCommerce metrics</strong> like total revenue, conversion rate, top products, and top referral sources. In a single report.</p>\n<p>Looking to engage with your customers or attract new ones? MonsterInsights has you covered.</p>\n<p>You can see exactly which content gets the <strong>most visits</strong>, has the most <strong>time spent on site</strong>, and that has the <strong>best bounce rate</strong>. This helps you <strong>analyze and optimize for better engagement</strong>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click here to get started with MonsterInsights today &#8211; 14-day, risk-free trial.</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"contact_form_plugins\">Best WordPress Contact Form Plugins &amp; Feedback Tools</h3>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">4. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-122207 aligncenter\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/wpforms-best-wordpress-forms-plugin.png\" alt=\"wpforms - best drag and drop wordpress form plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"408\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/wpforms-best-wordpress-forms-plugin.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/wpforms-best-wordpress-forms-plugin-300x197.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WPForms</a> has a drag and drop builder that makes it easy to create beautiful and highly-effective forms with cool features like smart conditional logic to provide an excellent user experience.</p>\n<p>Looking to respond to leads quickly?With WPForms you can receive instant email notifications for submitted forms to engage with leads right away.</p>\n<p>WPForms also offers several addons to enhance its already awesome features. You can easily connect with tools like PayPal, AWeber, MailChimp, and more.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Instant notifications whenever a form is submitted</li>\n<li>File uploads so visitors can provide whatever information you request</li>\n<li>Multi-page forms</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why You Need It:</strong></p>\n<p>Using a <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-wordpress-form-builder-plugins/\">contact form</a> keeps you looking professional, streamlines your communication with your site&#8217;s visitors, and helps you <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/beginners-guide-to-email-marketing/\">build your email list</a>.</p>\n<p>WPForms lets you build online forms and collect data effortlessly. No coding or design skills required.</p>\n<p>Using a contact form keeps you <strong>available to your site&#8217;s visitors</strong> without exposing your email address to spammers. With WPForms you get <strong>instant notification emails</strong> whenever a form is submitted and can <strong>customize the email subject line for each form</strong>. This makes it easy to organize your inbox.</p>\n<p>If you need to <strong>notify multiple people</strong>, you can do that too. Even better, you can <strong>customize who receives the notification</strong> based on how the user answers the form, saving your team time and reducing the time it takes to get in touch with your visitors.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get started with a risk-free, 14-day trial of WPForms!</a></p>\n<h3><a title=\"Formidable Forms\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/formidable-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">5. Formidable Forms</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Formidable Forms\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/formidable-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-129839\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/formidable-forms.png\" alt=\"formidable forms advanced wordpress form builder\" width=\"620\" height=\"302\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/formidable-forms.png 1201w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/formidable-forms-300x146.png 300w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/formidable-forms-768x374.png 768w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/formidable-forms-1024x499.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Formidable Forms\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/formidable-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Formidable Forms</a> is a versatile drag and drop form builder with great performance options.</p>\n<p>And, it lets you build interactive forms able to calculate problems in real time. So, a realtor could, for example, add a mortgage calculator to their site using Formidable Forms. That type of personalization drives visitors wild!</p>\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Calculated form fields make providing online estimates, calculating product options, or showing interest/repayment calculators a breeze</li>\n<li>Conditional redirection so you can route submission response notifications to the right people</li>\n<li>Automatically fill out forms to save time and increase conversions</li>\n<li>Cascading lookup fields display available options based on the selection from the previous form field</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why You Need It:</strong></p>\n<p>Formidable Forms also makes it super easy to collect and analyze data. Then, you can view that data in the form of charts, tables, and graphs. With such simple access to optin performance, you can use a data-driven approach toward mailing list optimization.</p>\n<p>But wait, there&#8217;s more!Formidable Forms integrates with the WordPress eCommerce plugin WooCommerce. There, it can be used to collect customer information, calculate prices based on upsells and shipping, as well as other features to drive sales and improve the customer experience.</p>\n<h3><a title=\"LiveChat Inc\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">6. LiveChat</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"LiveChat Inc\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-133089\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/livechat-wordpress-plugin.png\" alt=\"livechat wordpress plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"270\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/livechat-wordpress-plugin.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/livechat-wordpress-plugin-300x131.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The <a title=\"LiveChat Inc\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">LiveChat WordPress plugin</a> lets you quickly and easily add live chat support to your WordPress website that your visitors can use to get instant answers to their questions and concerns.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>File sharing and chat transcripts</li>\n<li>Smart or manual chat routing</li>\n<li>Feedback from users (chat/ticket ratings, post-chat surveys, satisfaction stats)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>LiveChat has tons of customization options, a mobile app, and integrates with the other tools you&#8217;re using, making it an invaluable piece of your sales and marketing platform.</p>\n<p><a title=\"LiveChat Inc\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Click here to get started with LiveChat for free.</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-mail-smtp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">7. WP Mail SMTP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-mail-smtp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"size-large wp-image-132994 aligncenter\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/wp-mail-smtp-best-wordpress-plugins-min.png\" alt=\"best wordpress plugins - WP Mail SMTP\" width=\"620\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/wp-mail-smtp-best-wordpress-plugins-min.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/wp-mail-smtp-best-wordpress-plugins-min-300x97.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Ever have issues with receiving notifications from your WordPress site? <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-mail-smtp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">WP Mail SMTP</a> can fix that. This plugin reconfigured WordPress to use more reliable methods to send your emails.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Quick and easy setup, even for beginners &#8211; no code needed</li>\n<li>Choose from several SMTP providers including Mailgun, SendGrid, Gmail, and more</li>\n<li>Stop missing out on contact form notifications</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why You Need It:</strong></p>\n<p>The way that WordPress is set up by default, the emails that it sends aren&#8217;t properly authenticated. If the proper authentication isnt there, then those emails either go in your spam folder or don&#8217;t get delivered at all.</p>\n<p>This includes emails such as new comment notifications, new user registration emails, and even your contact form notifications. For small businesses, it can really hurt your bottom line if your WordPress form notifications aren&#8217;t reaching your inbox.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s why it&#8217;s so important to use WP Mail SMTP if your WordPress notifications aren&#8217;t working.</p>\n<p><a title=\"WP Mail SMTP\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-mail-smtp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click here to get started with WP Mail SMTP for free.</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"affiliate_marketing_plugins\">Best Affiliate Marketing Plugins for WordPress</h3>\n<h3><a title=\"Pretty Links Pro\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/pretty-links-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">8. Pretty Links</a></h3>\n<p><a title=\"Pretty Links Pro\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/refer/pretty-links-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-121925\" src=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/pretty_links.png\" alt=\"pretty_links affiliate link plugin to easily create pretty links\" width=\"620\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/pretty_links.png 620w, https://optinmonster.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/pretty_links-300x137.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Create short links that are actually readable, speakable, and memorable. With <a title=\"Pretty Links Pro\" href=\"https://optinmonster.com/r